26quot%3B%3A%20Army%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20geopolitical%20landscape%20is%20facing%20unprecedented%20changes%20and%20today%20nations%20have%20shown%20the%20willingness%20to%20use%20hard%20power%2C%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20said%20at%20the%20maiden%20NDTV%20Defence%20Summit%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20chief%20said%20the%20centrality%20of%20national%20interest%20and%20the%20growing%20salience%20of%20national%20security%20in%20the%20international%20system%20are%20distinctly%20visible.%20Today%20Nations%20have%20shown%20willingness%20to%20resort%20to%20the%20use%20of%20heart%20power%20to%20secure%20their%20interest.%20A%20situation%20of%20return%20to%20conflict%20to%20achieve%20political%20and%20military%20objectives.%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BWhile%20conventional%20warfare%20has%20gone%20under%20changes%2C%20emerging%20technologies%20today%20are%20not%20central%20only%20to%20rich%20nations.%20Disruptive%20technology%20is%20transforming%20warfare.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAsymmetry%20In%20Warfare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20modern%20technologies%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20superpowers%20but%20non-state%20actors%20can%20access%20such%20technology.%20The%20asymmetry%20in%20conflict%20has%20increased%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20fallout%20with%20an%20increased%20propensity%20of%20risk-taking%20behaviour%20to%20initiate%20a%20low-threshold%20armed%20conflict%2C%20the%20army%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Pande%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20legacy%20challenges%20of%20unsettled%20borders%20continue%20and%20newer%20threats%20in%20the%20spectrum%20of%20conflict%20have%20added%20complexity%20and%20the%20grey%20zone%20actions%20and%20aggressions%20from%20adversaries%20are%20manifesting%20across%20domains%20-%20Land%2C%20sea%2C%20and%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmy's%20Vision%20For%20Future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Pande%20stressed%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20need%20to%20secure%20our%20national%20interest%20and%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20possessing%20capabilities%20that%20require%20continuous%20progression.%20Highlighting%20the%20vision%20of%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20COAS%20said%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20a%20large%20land-based%20force%2C%20has%20to%20transform%20into%20an%20agile%2C%20future-ready%20force%20that%20can%20operate%20in%20a%20multi-domain%20environment%20and%20have%20synergy%20with%20other%20forces.%20These%20elements%20are%20important%20for%20the%20force%20to%20be%20future-ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20Chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSwadeshikaran%20(indigenisation)%20se%20sashaktikaran%20(empowerment)%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20All%20sectors%20have%20a%20crucial%20role%20to%20play.%20It%20is%20essential%20to%20develop%20core%20competencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAatmanirbharta%20or%20self-reliance%20in%20defence%20manufacturing%20and%20procurement%20has%20been%20a%20vision%20as%20well%20as%20a%20goal%20of%20governments.%20The%20Indigenous%20defense%20industry%20is%20critical%20for%20war-fighting%20capability.%20The%20Army%20Chief%20said%20the%20disruption%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20has%20highlighted%20how%20wars%20can%20disrupt%20in%20supply%20of%20technology%20and%20weapons%20and%20it%20also%20entails%20the%20risk%20that%20nations%20may%20not%20transfer%20critical%20technology.%20To%20pursue%20our%20aspirations%2C%20self-reliance%20is%20important%20and%20sustenance%20of%20the%20existing%20ones%20is%20necessary%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transformational%20nature%20of%20war%20hybridization%20of%20threats%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20cyber%20war%20has%20brought%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20development%20of%20safeguarding%20platforms%20with%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArtificial%20Intelligence%2C%20Machine%20Learning%2C%20Cyber%20biotechnology%2C%20and%20space%20-%20It%20is%20essential%20to%20harness%20these%20technologies%20and%20use%20them%20in%20defense%2C%20the%20Army%20Chief%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20our%20technological%20prowess%20has%20been%20a%20driver%20for%20global%20tech.%20The%20government%20has%20taken%20initiatives%20to%20promote%20an%20effective%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20country%20that%20enables%20simplification%20of%20industry%20in%20licensing%2C%20foreign%20investment%2C%20and%20Research%20and%20Development%20projects.%20The%20establishment%20of%20defence%20corridors%20and%20others%20are%20such%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709807160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fq41qcp7_army-chief-1200_625x300_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-pande-says-world-is-seeing-a-situation-of-return-to-conflict-to-achieve-political-objectives-5193381%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20geopolitical%20landscape%20is%20facing%20unprecedented%20changes%20and%20today%20nations%20have%20shown%20the%20willingness%20to%20use%20hard%20power%2C%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-pande-says-world-is-seeing-a-situation-of-return-to-conflict-to-achieve-political-objectives-5193381%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-pande-says-world-is-seeing-a-situation-of-return-to-conflict-to-achieve-political-objectives-5193381%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-pande-says-world-is-seeing-a-situation-of-return-to-conflict-to-achieve-political-objectives-5193381%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSuspicious%26quot%3B%20IMPS%20Transactions%20Worth%20Rs%20820%20Crore%20Found%2C%20CBI%20Searches%20