2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68498472%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Niger's%20army%20chief%20says%20it%20will%20be%20operational%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20without%20giving%20details%20of%20its%20size.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68498472%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68498472.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68498472.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Rally%20vs%20Rally%20Counter%20After%20PM's%20Sandeshkhali%20Offensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20fired%20barbs%20at%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20over%20the%20raging%20Sandeshkhali%20issue%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20today%20led%20a%20rally%20of%20women%20supporters%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20some%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20which%20has%20made%20headlines%20for%20the%20serious%20allegations%20against%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders%2C%20also%20took%20part%20in%20the%20rally.%20The%20theme%20of%20the%20rally%20is%20Mahilader%20Adhikar%2C%20Amader%20Angikar%20(women's%20rights%2C%20our%20commitment).%20The%20rally%20is%20in%20signature%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20style%20-%20a%20foot%20march%20with%20her%20at%20the%20front.%20Among%20the%20prominent%20women%20Trinamool%20leaders%20to%20join%20her%20are%20Sushmita%20Dev%2C%20Shashi%20Panja%20and%20the%20party's%20newly-elected%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20journalist%20Sagarika%20Ghose.%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20nephew%20and%20the%20party's%20national%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20also%20joined%20the%20march.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20rally%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20said%20women%20are%20tortured%20in%20Bengal.%20I%20can%20challenge%20that%20women%20are%20the%20safest%20in%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20without%20naming%20him%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20was%20he%20when%20women%20were%20paraded%20naked%20in%20Manipur%2C%20when%20a%20woman%20was%20raped%20and%20her%20body%20forcibly%20cremated%20in%20Hathras%3F%20Have%20you%20forgotten%20Bilkis%20(Bano)%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20also%20responded%20to%20former%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20judge%20Abhijt%20Gangopadhyay%20joining%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BA%20BJP%20babu%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20bench%20and%20he%20joined%20BJP.%20How%20can%20you%20expect%20justice%20from%20them%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20leads%20a%20march%20of%20women%20to%20mark%20the%20International%20Women's%20Day%20on%20March%208.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20the%20rally%20is%20being%20held%20on%20March%207.%20It%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20date%20change%20is%20Shiv%20Ratri%2C%20which%20will%20be%20celebrated%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20voters%20form%20a%20key%20support%20base%20for%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20Over%20the%2013%20years%20that%20the%20party%20has%20stayed%20in%20power%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20has%20consolidated%20this%20support%20base%20through%20schemes%20such%20as%20Kanyashri%2C%20Rupashree%20and%20Lakshmir%20Bhandar.%20But%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20episode%20and%20BJP's%20aggressive%20campaign%20threatens%20to%20divide%20this%20voter%20base%2C%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20taking%20no%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20BJP's%20Mahila%20Morcha%20event%20in%20Barasat%20yesterday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20described%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-women%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20said%20women%20in%20Bengal%20are%20outraged%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bstorm%20of%20Sandeshkhali%26quot%3B%20won't%20remain%20restricted%20to%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20spread%20across%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20Bengal%20government%20is%20using%20all%20its%20might%20to%20protect%20Sandeshkhali%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20the%20CBI's%20custody.%20Sandeshkhali%20residents%20have%20accused%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20allegations%20surfaced%20and%20the%20BJP%20raised%20a%20political%20storm%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20had%2C%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20the%20Assembly%20on%20February%2015%2C%20hit%20back%20and%20accused%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20of%20targeting%20Shahjahan.%20But%20as%20the%20issue%20garnered%20national%20attention%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20changed%20tack%20and%20arrested%20the%20strongman.%20He%20was%20also%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20for%20six%20years.%20The%20Trinamool%20then%20tried%20to%20turn%20the%20tables%20on%20the%20BJP%2C%20daring%20it%20to%20act%20against%20leaders%20who%20face%20serious%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Trinamool's%20response%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20remarks%20yesterday%2C%20party%20leader%20Derek%20O'Brien%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20lectured%20on%20Nari%20Shakti.%20Three%20questions%20to%20you%2C%20Sir%20-%20Why%20are%20there%2051%20cases%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20every%20hour%3F%20Why%20does%20BJP%20have%2013%20per%20cent%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20why%20only%2014%20per%20cent%20women%20in%20195%20candidate%20list%3F%20Why%20no%20action%20against%20BJP%20MP%20charged%20with%20sexually%20harassing%20wrestlers%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20Trinamool%20leader%20was%20referring%20to%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20to%20step%20down%20as%20the%20national%20wrestling%20federation%20chief%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2