oleon%26quot%3B%20action%20figures%20or%20fast-food%20tie-ins.%20And%20since%20the%20Apple-made%20movies%20are%20expressly%20built%20to%20be%20shown%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-tv-plus-shows%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20TV%2B%3C%2Fa%3E%20streaming%20service%2C%20Apple%20can't%20make%20money%20selling%20them%20to%20a%20different%20streamer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20leaves%20video-on-demand%20sales%2C%20where%20Apple%20and%20other%20distributors%20sell%20or%20rent%20the%20movies%20digitally.%20But%20those%20numbers%20should%20be%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20box-office%20receipts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20asked%20Apple%20PR%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20expect%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Henry%20Cavill%2C%20Dua%20Lipa%2C%20Bryce%20Dallas%20Howard%20and%20Sam%20Rockwell%20attend%20the%20Global%20Premiere%20of%20the%20Apple%20Original%20Film.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e8f3e7ce7f1785b2e7333c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenry%20Cavill%2C%20Dua%20Lipa%2C%20Bryce%20Dallas%20Howard%2C%20and%20Sam%20Rockwell%20at%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BArgylle.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EDave%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20that%20somewhere%20in%20Apple's%20accounting%20department%2C%20someone%20has%20agreed%20to%20say%20that%20big%2C%20splashy%20movies%20with%20some%20degree%20of%20critical%20acclaim%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BNapoleon%26quot%3B%20is%20up%20for%20a%20few%20Oscars%3B%20%26quot%3BKillers%26quot%3B%20is%20up%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20them%2C%20including%20best%20picture%20and%20best%20director%20%E2%80%94%20generates%20marketing%20value%20for%20Apple%20in%20general%20and%20Apple%20TV%2B%20specifically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20that's%20GAAP%20accounting%2C%20but%20whatever.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs2.q4cdn.com%2F470004039%2Ffiles%2Fdoc_earnings%2F2023%2Fq4%2Ffiling%2F_10-K-Q4-2023-As-Filed.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20made%20%2497%20billion%20in%20%3Cem%3Eprofit%3C%2Fem%3E%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20can%20chalk%20the%20entire%20cost%20of%20its%20film%20slate%20up%20to%20marketing%20and%20call%20it%20a%20day%20if%20it%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EApple%2C%20movies%2C%20and%20TV%3A%20Why%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%2C%20yet-to-be-answered%20question%3A%20Why%20is%20Apple%20making%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20at%20all%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20obvious%20answer%20is%20that%20it%20needs%20things%20for%20its%20Apple%20TV%2B%20streaming%20service.%20And%20the%20second%20obvious%20answer%20is%20that%20Apple%20needs%20Apple%20TV%2B%20because%20it's%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20making%20money%20from%20%26quot%3Bservices%26quot%3B%20as%20iPhone%20sales%20slow%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20remember%20%E2%80%94%20the%20primary%20driver%20for%20%26quot%3Bservices%26quot%3B%20is%20really%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20paying%20for%20in-app%20purchases%20in%20games%20they%20downloaded%20from%20Apple's%20App%20Store%2C%26quot%3B%20plus%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2F23933206%2Fgoogle-apple-search-deal-safari-18-billion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2418%20billion%20Google%20pays%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20managed%20to%20grow%20Apple%20TV%2B%20meaningfully%20after%20a%20rocky%20start.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20subscription-tracking%20service%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitaltrends.com%2Fhome-theater%2Fmost-popular-streaming-services-by-subscribers%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DApple%2520TV%252B%253A%252025%2520million%2520(estimated)%2C-Apple%2520TV%252B%2520is%26amp%3Btext%3DEstimates%2520from%2520market%2520research%2520firm%2Cto%2520purchases%2520of%2520Apple%2520hardware.)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAntenna%20estimated%20that%20the%20company%20had%20about%2025%20million%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20nothing%20compared%20with%20Netflix's%20260%20million%20subscribers%2C%20but%20it%20is%20definitely%20something%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20Apple%20is%20charging%20%2410%20a%20month%20for%20the%20service%20in%20the%20US%20(like%20its%20peers%2C%20it%20charges%20considerably%20less%20in%20some%20international%20markets).%20Still%2C%20even%20in%20the%20best-case%20scenario%2C%20Apple%20TV%2B%20is%20a%20sliver%20of%20the%20%2485%20billion%20Apple%20made%20from%20services%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20look%3A%20I'm%20not%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-earnings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20shareholder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20am%20someone%20who%20likes%20to%20see%20movies.%20And%20I%20kinda%20liked%20%26quot%3BNapoleon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20one%20of%20my%20kids%20thought%20%26quot%3BArgylle%26quot%3B%20was%20not%20bad%20(I%20love%20him%2C%20but%20he's%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40pkafka%2Fpost%2FC28QPTyPXpl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eawful%3C%2Fa%3E).%20And%20one%20day%20when%20I%20have%20four%20hours%20free%2C%20I'll%20watch%20Martin%20Scorsese's%20latest%20movie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq.com%2Fstory%2Fmartin-scorsese-profile%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecause%20he's%20not%20going%20to%20make%20many%20more%20movies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20keep%20making%20this%20stuff%2C%20Apple!%20You%20can%20afford%20it%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20you%20define%20%26quot%3Bprofit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-movies-napoleon-argylle-killers-flower-moon-box-office-profits-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3