%3Eplant-based%20meats%20still%20cost%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20their%20animal-derived%20equivalents%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elike%20the%20NotHotDog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20manufacturers%20like%20Beyond%20Meat%20and%20Impossible%20Foods%20have%20refined%20their%20recipes%20and%20manufacturing%20processes%20to%20become%20more%20efficient%20over%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20making%20soy%2C%20corn%2C%20and%20other%20ingredients%20taste%20like%20meat%20is%20still%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20parts%20of%20the%20process%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.new-foodinnovation.co.uk%2Fprice-parity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20by%20New%20Food%20Innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20UK-based%20startup%20accelerator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20own%2C%20soy%20and%20other%20ingredients%20tend%20to%20be%20much%20cheaper%20than%20animal%20meats%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20But%20the%20fats%2C%20oils%2C%20flavorings%2C%20and%20other%20additions%20that%20make%20a%20plant-based%20burger%20look%20and%20taste%20like%20beef%20or%20other%20meats%20represent%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20cost.%20Meantime%2C%20the%20plant-based%20proteins%20themselves%20account%20for%20about%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeef%20as%20an%20ingredient%20is%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20with%20inbuilt%20flavor%2C%20structure%20and%20fat%2C%20which%20plant-based%20options%20find%20costly%20to%20replicate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyond-meat-vegan-plant-based-fake-meat-inflation-prices-restaurants-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFood%20inflation%20has%20also%20hit%20plant-based%20meat%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20some%20consumers%20picking%20less%20expensive%20forms%20of%20protein%20to%20save%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetailers%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20narrow%20the%20price%20gap.%20Nearly