h%20you%20to%20not%20turn%20this%20country%20into%20a%20living%20hell.%20With%20you%20not%20have%20to%20show%20your%20faces%20and%20confront%20your%20conscience%20some%20day%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20can%20peaceably%20settle%20our%20differences%20there%20is%20still%20hope%20that%20we%20can%20co-exist%20as%20brothers.%20Otherwise%20there%20is%20no%20hope.%20If%20you%20choose%20the%20other%20path%2C%20we%20may%20never%20come%20face%20one%20another%20again.%20For%20now%2C%20I%20have%20just%20one%20thing%20to%20ask%20of%20you%3A%20Give%20up%20any%20thoughts%20of%20enslaving%20this%20country%20under%20military%20rule%20again!%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask%20my%20people%20to%20immediately%20set%20up%20committees%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%20to%20carry%20on%20our%20struggle%20in%20ever%20neighborhood%2C%20village%2C%20union%20and%20subdivision%20of%20this%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20must%20prepare%20yourselves%20now%20with%20what%20little%20you%20have%20for%20the%20struggle%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20have%20given%20blood%2C%20we%20will%20give%20more%20of%20it.%20But%2C%20Insha%E2%80%99Allah%2C%20we%20will%20free%20the%20people%20of%20this%20land!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20struggle%20this%20time%20is%20for%20emancipation!%20The%20struggle%20this%20time%20is%20for%20independence!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20ready.%20We%20cannot%20afford%20to%20lose%20our%20momentum.%20Keep%20the%20movement%20and%20the%20struggle%20alive%20because%20if%20we%20fall%20back%20the%20will%20come%20down%20hard%20upon%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20disciplined.%20No%20nation%E2%80%99s%20movement%20can%20be%20victorious%20without%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoy%20Bangla!%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709803807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07140906%2F12109456696_e1f1a688fa_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwhat-i-want-is-justice-sheikh-mujibur-rahmans-spe