0glorious%20past%20when%20Pushpak%20Vimans%20and%20even%20interplanetary%20travel%20prevailed.%20Such%20claims%20from%20mythology%20being%20true%20abound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20are%20such%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20being%20taught%20in%20the%20schools%20but%20they%20are%20also%20determining%20the%20allocation%20of%20funds%20for%20science%20and%20technology%20research.%20Huge%20funds%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F35cd7074-cafa-47f2-a2ca-e47d51fcbc1c%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F35cd7074-cafa-47f2-a2ca-e47d51fcbc1c%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709879883760000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0Xu1TH7eoUU1fMQwuw16h4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20deployed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20IIT%20Delhi%20for%20research%20into%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPanchgavya%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20five%20products%20from%20cows%3A%20milk%2C%20curd%2C%20ghee%20(clarified%20butter)%2C%20urine%20and%20dung.%20This%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20panacea%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20various%20diseases.%20Cow%20urine%20is%20being%20promoted%20separately%20as%20being%20of%20medicinal%20use.%20Even%20before%20this%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20parent%20organisation%20RSS%20floated%20many%20organisations%20to%20promote%20faith-based%20knowledge%20through%20school%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinanath%20Batra%20has%20been%20heading%20the%20Shiksha%20Bachao%20Abhiyan%20Samiti%20and%20the%20RSS-affiliated%20Shiksha%20Sanskriti%20Utthan%20Nyas%20(SSUN)%20for%20many%20decades.%20His%20nine%20books%20have%20been%20translated%20into%20Gujarati%20and%20introduced%20in%2042%2C000%20schools%20in%20Gujarat.%20A%20sampling%20of%20Batra%E2%80%99s%20books%20gives%20a%20good%20idea%20of%20what%20is%20being%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20quote%20from%20one%20of%20the%20sets%20of%20books%2C%20%E2%80%98Tejonmaya%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20(Radiant%20Bharat)%20tells%20us%20about%20one%20Dr%20Balkrishna%20Ganpat%20Matapurkar%20whose%20research%20has%20been%20inspired%20by%20the%20Mahabharata.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20Gandhari%E2%80%99s%20womb%20delivered%20a%20huge%20mass%20of%20flesh.%20Dwaipayan%20Vyas%20was%20called.%20He%20observed%20this%20hard%20mass%20of%20flesh%20and%20then%20preserved%20it%20in%20a%20cold%20tank%20with%20specific%20medicines.%20He%20then%20divided%20the%20mass%20of%20flesh%20into%20100%20parts%20and%20kept%20them%20separately%20in%20100%20tanks%20full%20of%20ghee%20for%20two%20years.%20After%20two%20years%2C%20100%20Kauravas%20were%20born%20of%20it.%20On%20reading%20this%2C%20he%20(Matapurkar)%20realised%20that%20stem%20cell%20technology%20was%20part%20of%20Indian%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20Indian%20rishis%2C%20using%20yoga%20vidya%2C%20would%20attain%C2%A0%3Cem%3Edivya%20drishti%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(divine%20vision).%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20invention%20of%20television%20goes%20back%20to%20this%E2%80%A6%20In%20the%20Mahabharata%2C%20Sanjaya%20sitting%20inside%20a%20palace%20in%20Hastinapur%20and%20using%20his%C2%A0%3Cem%3Edivya%20shakti%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(divine%20power)%20would%20give%20a%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20battle%20of%20Mahabharata%E2%80%A6%20to%20the%20blind%20Dhritarashtra.%20(Page%2064)%20What%20we%20know%20today%20as%20the%20motorcar%20existed%20during%20the%20Vedic%20period.%20It%20was%20called%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eanashva%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0rath.%20Usually%20a%20rath%20(chariot)%20is%20pulled%20by%20horses%20but%20an%20anashva%20rath%20means%20the%20one%20that%20runs%20without%20horses%20or%20yantra-rath%2C%20which%20is%20today%20a%20motorcar.%20The%20Rig%20Veda%20refers%20to%20this%2C%20he%20claims.%20(Page%2060)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20has%20also%20set%20up%20a%20consultative%20body%20called%20Bharatiya%20Shiksha%20Niti%20Ayog%20(BSNA)%2C%20whose%20policies%20are%20guiding%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccorrect%20or%20Indianize%E2%80%9D%20the%20national%20education%20system.%20Now%20organisations%20like%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Historical%20Research%2C%20National%20Council%20for%20Education%2C%20Research%20and%20Training%20amongst%20others%2C%20have%20got%20heads%20whose%20qualification%20is%20not%20excellence%20in%20their%20disciplines%20but%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20recall%20one%20Y.Sudarshan%20who%20was%20appointed%20as%20chief%20of%20ICHR.%20He%20was%20out%20to%20prove%20the%20historicity%20of%20our%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Ff550418a-8df9-49ad-a5cb-bf97d6c6130e%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Ff550418a-8df9-49ad-a5cb-bf97d6c6130e%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709879883760000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0xr1tA8wpDWf8UH_Xv2QVt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0mythological%20epics%2C%20the%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20promoting%20Baba%20Ramdev%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20We%20recall%20how%20his%20Coronil%2C%20claiming%20to%20be%20a%20treatment%20for%20Covid%20was%20promoted.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20recently%20given%20a%20verdict%20whereby%20Ramdev%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F14e6d56b-a4a4-423c-b075-adf037d52bd5%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F14e6d56b-a4a4-423c-b075-adf037d52bd5%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709879883760000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3zHH3W9OgzFEubaNm25LaF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0warned%20not%20to%20advertise%20irrational%20products%20and%20misleading%20ads%20about%20the%20modern%20system%20of%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20has%20for%20the%20past%20many%20years%20been%20accepting%20papers%20which%20have%20no%20scientific%20basis%20and%20are%20based%20on%20mythology.%20Pained%20by%20this%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F59d65ac7-cdf7-45d0-9123-d6d0a9af769c%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F59d65ac7-cdf7-45d0-9123-d6d0a9af769c%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709879883760000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw12vI1ZT8GA2Rq0KptNO9OE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprominent%20scientists%20have%20come%20together%20and%20issued%20a%20statement%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ecalling%20upon%20the%20government%20to%20stop%20undermining%20scientific%20methods%20and%20thinking.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20point%20out%20that%20this%20attitude%20has%20been%20particularly%20evident%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20promotion%20of%20unverified%20or%20unscientific%20ideas%2C%20exaggeration%20of%20ancient%20Indian%20knowledge%2C%20and%20certain%20responses%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%E2%80%9D%20And%20further%20the%20statement%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20emphasizes%20the%20need%20for%20a%20united%20front%20among%20scientists%2C%20academics%2C%20and%20policymakers%20to%20combat%20the%20erosion%20of%20scientific%20integrity%20and%20promote%20rational%2C%20evidence-based%20discourse%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20our%20Constitution%20mandates%20the%20promotion%20of%20scientific%20temper%2C%20the%20present%20regime%20in%20matters%20of%20policy-making%20is%20bypassing%20the%20rational%20approach%20not%20only%20in%20science%20research%20and%20education%20but%20also%20in%20matters%20related%20to%20social%20policies.%20In%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy%202020%2C%20there%20is%20a%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Knowledge%20Systems%E2%80%99.%20This%20basically%20means%20promotion%20of%20faith%20based%20understanding%20of%20knowledge%20related%20to%20material%20and%20social%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20political%20streams%20which%20support%20the%20movement%20for%20social%20change%20towards%20equality%20try%20to%20adopt%20rational%20and%20scientific%20approaches%20to%20knowledge%20and%20social%20issues%2C%20the%20major%20examples%20being%20Gautam%20Buddha%2C%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Ambedkar%20and%20Nehru%20in%20particular.%20Throughout%20Indian%20history%20those%20who%20want%20to%20impose%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20social%20relations%2C%20those%20who%20want%20to%20maintain%20relations%20of%20inequality%20generally%20resort%20to%20faith%20based%20knowledge%2C%20taking%20mythology%20as%20the%20gospel%20truth%20and%20imposing%20it%20on%20society.%20The%20communal%20fundamental%20streams%20accept%20technology%20with%20great%20avidity%2C%20even%20as%20they%20dislike%20rational%20thinking%20and%20the%20scientific%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20of%20these%20outstanding%20scientists%20is%20a%20timely%20urge%20to%20implement%20social%20and%20science%20policies%20founded%20on%20reason%2C%20on%20scientific%20temper.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709800150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F12204307%2Funnamed.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmajoritarian-nationalism-is-undermining-indias-science-policies-potential%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20our%20Constitution%20mandates%20the%20promotion%20of%20scientific%20temper%2C%20the%20present%20regime%20in%20matters%20of%20policy-making%20is%20bypassing%20the%20rational%20approach%20not%20only%20in%20science%20research%20and%20education%20but%20also%20in%20matters%20related%20to%20social%20policies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmajoritarian-nationalism-is-undermining-indias-science-policies-potential%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20just%20pulled%20the%20country%20version%20of%20a%20company%20canceling%20its%20quarterly%20earnings%20call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang(L)%20bows%20to%20delegates%20during%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20fourth%20plenary%20session%20of%20the%20National%20People's%20Congress%20on%20March%2011%2C%202023%20in%20Beijing%2C%20China.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e942aace7f1785b2e738b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChinese%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20and%20Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping.%3Cp%3ELintao%20Zhang%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20has%20canceled%20a%20closely%20watched%20annual%20press%20conference%20with%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20cancellation%20comes%20amid%20concerns%20about%20China's%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20suggest%20the%20move%20indicates%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20attempting%20to%20control%20the%20narrative%20regarding%20China's%20economic%20health.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20few%20people%20have%20insight%20into%20what%20really%20makes%20it%20tick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20pre