2%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Have%20Already%20Crossed%20370%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajnath%20Singh%20Quips%20On%20Poll%20Question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20witty%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20BJP's%20target%20to%20win%20370%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20today%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20crossed%20370%26quot%3B%20-%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%202019%20move%20to%20remove%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20was%20speaking%20to%20NDTV's%20editor-in-chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20during%20NDTV's%20maiden%20Defence%20Summit.%20His%20370%20quip%20came%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20370-seats%20target%20the%20BJP%20has%20set%20for%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20repeated%20the%20party's%20slogans%20of%20%26quot%3BNDA%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBJP%20370%20paar%26quot%3B.%20He%20then%20added%20with%20a%20smile%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20understand%20370%20very%20well%2C%20we%20have%20already%20crossed%20370.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%20and%20southern%20states%20are%20tough%20terrains%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20tough%20at%20all.%20You%20must%20have%20seen%20our%20condition%20in%20West%20Bengal%20before%202014.%20We%20would%20not%20win%20a%20single%20seat.%20In%202019%2C%20we%20won%2018%20seats.%20And%20this%20time%2C%20one%20cannot%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20that%20BJP%20may%20win%20between%2025%20and%2030%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20southern%20states%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20trust%20of%20people%20in%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20grown.%20%26quot%3BYou%20must%20have%20seen%20how%20masses'%20support%20for%20our%20Prime%20Minister.%20Not%20just%20him%2C%20we%20too%20get%20a%20great%20response%20and%20this%20boosts%20our%20confidence%20that%20achieving%20the%20target%20we%20have%20set%20won't%20be%20a%20difficult%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20the%20BJP%20'importing'%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20there%20are%20many%20leaders%20in%20the%20Opposition%20who%20want%20the%20country%20to%20move%20forward.%20%26quot%3BThey%20feel%20that%20their%20party%20is%20not%20in%20a%20state%20to%20take%20the%20country%20forward.%20Only%20BJP%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20can%20take%20the%20country%20forward.%20So%2C%20they%20are%20coming%20to%20us%20and%20we%20welcome%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20that%20only%20the%20Opposition%20is%20responsible%20for%20its%20weakening.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BJP's%20plan%20to%20reach%20every%20voter%2C%20he%20said%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20party's%20grassroots%20workers%20is%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20common%20man.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20ground%20level%2C%20we%20have%20panna%20pramukhs.%20His%20work%20is%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20with%20only%2010-15%20families.%20We%20have%20a%20robust%20and%20effective%20system%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20politician%20said%20the%20BJP%20also%20carried%20out%20a%20nationwide%20yatra%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20eligible%20person%20gets%20benefits%20of%20the%20Centre's%20welfare%20schemes.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20planned%20down%20to%20that%20level.%20If%20anyone%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20benefits%2C%20immediate%20assistance%20is%20provided%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20addressing%20NDTV's%20first%20Defence%20Summit%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20prioritised%20the%20defence%20sector%20and%20encouraged%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20we%20put%20defence%20sector%20as%20our%20main%20priority.%20Atmanirbharta%20(self-reliance)%20was%20encouraged%20and%20we%20introduced%20many%20Make-in-India%20initiatives.%20Our%20focus%20was%20on%20military%20modernisation%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20saying%20that%20previous%20governments%20did%20not%20put%20emphasis%20on%20defence%20sector.%20But%20we%20brought%20atmanirbharta%20in%20the%20defence%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709798640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Firpv9cdo_rajnath-singh-ndtv-defence-summit-650-_650x400_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-ndtv-defence-summit-we-have-already-crossed-370-rajnath-singh-quips-on-poll-question-5192724%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20witty%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20BJP's%20target%20to%20win%20370%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20today%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20crossed%20370%26quot%3B%20-%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20the%202019%20move%20to%20remove%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-ndtv-defence-summit-we-have-already-crossed-370-rajnath-singh-quips-on-poll-question-5192724%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-ndtv-defence-summit-we-have-already-crossed-370-rajnath-singh-quips-on-poll-question-5192724%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-ndtv-defence-summit-we-have-already-crossed-370-rajnath-singh-quips-on-poll-question-5192724%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seven%20Years%20on%2C%20Jalpaiguri%20Child%20Trafficking%20Victims%20Await%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07125130%2Fhudson-hintze-vpxeE7s-my4-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalpaiguri%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20has%20been%20over%20eight%20years%20since%20Kajal%20Basfor%20last%20saw%20her%20son%2C%20Ganesh.%20In%202016%2C%20Ganesh%20ran%20away%20after%20facing%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20scolding%20and%20a%20beating.%20As%20per%20the%20Child%20Helpline%20record%2C%20he%20was%20found%20at%20New%20Jalpaiguri%20Station%20in%20North%20Bengal%2C%20following%20which%20the%20police%20took%20him%20to%20a%20temporary%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKajal%20came%20to%20Jalpaiguri%20hoping%20for%20a%20reunion%2C%20but%20was%20instead%20locked%20up%20at%20a%20shelter%20home%20called%20Ashraya.%20Her%20three-year-old%20daughter%20Dipali%20was%20forcefully%20taken%20away%20to%20another%20shelter%20home%2C%20Bimala%20Shishu%20Griha.%20While%20Kajal%20was%20released%20after%20a%20few%20days%2C%20Dipali%20was%20held%20captive%20at%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20help%2C%20Kajal%20and%20her%20husband%20approached%20the%20Jalpaiguri%20Child%20Welfare%20Centre%20and%20the%20district%20collector.%20The%20Child%20Welfare%20Centre%20clarified%20that%20two%20members%20of%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%2C%20seeing%20Kajal%E2%80%99s%20emotional%20state%2C%20deemed%20her%20unfit%20to%20raise%20a%20child%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20separation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKajal%20finally%20got%20to%20reunite%20with%20her%20daughter%20after%20a%20few%20months%2C%20but%20the%20search%20for%20Ganesh%20is%20still%20on.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20returned%20my%20daughter%20as%20she%20looks%20a%20lot%20like%20me.%20I%20heard%20that%20my%20son%20is%20living%20at%20a%20home%2C%20but%20I%20am%20yet%20to%20meet%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kajal%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Birpara%2C%20around%2063%20km%20from%20Jalpaiguri%20town%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20nearby%20Siliguri%2C%20Sanu%20Das%20is%20waiting%20to%20reunite%20with%20her%20daughter.%20Her%20two%20daughters%2C%20aged%20five%20and%20eight%2C%20went%20missing%20in%202016%20while%20she%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital.%20Despite%20extensive%20searching%2C%20Sanu%20Das%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20her%20daughters%20and%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20Darjeeling%20Legal%20Aid%20Forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jalpaiguri%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20initiated%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20short-stay%20homes%20where%20children%20were%20being%20taken.%20While%20one%20of%20the%20children%20was%20found%20at%20a%20shelter%20home%2C%20police%20investigations%20revealed%20that%20the%20younger%20child%20was%20sold%20to%20a%20childless%20couple.%20The%20CID%20summoned%20the%20couple%20to%20the%20Jalpaiguri%20CWC%2C%20where%20Sanu%20identified%20her%20daughter%20and%20demanded%20her%20return.%20However%2C%20the%20adoptive%20family%20is%20reluctant%20to%20relinquish%20rights%20over%20the%20child.%20In%20booth%20these%20cases%2C%20the%20shelter%20homes%20were%20being%20run%20by%20a%20teacher-turned-NGO%20owner%2C%20Chandana%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%2C%20and%20where%20it%20is%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Jalpaiguri%20town%20was%20rocked%20by%20a%20large-scale%20child%20trafficking%20racket%20run%20by%20an%20orphanage%20owner%20with%20political%20connections.%20Seven%20years%20later%2C%20the%20CID%20is%20yet%20to%20file%20the%20final%20chargesheet%20even%20as%20three%20of%20the%20seven%20accused%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20are%20out%20on%20bail.%20As%20per%20records%2C%20during%20this%20time%2C%20the%20CID%20has%20questioned%2033%20of%20the%2073%20witnesses%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20taken%20charge%20recently.%20Seven%20people%20were%20arrested%20during%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20the%20case%20%E2%80%93%20two%20were%20child%20welfare%20officials.%20The%20government%20officials%20are%20still%20in%20jail.%20Some%20politicians%20were%20also%20questioned.%20But%20my%20predecessor%20would%20know%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chayan%20Bhattacherjee%2C%20district%20inspector%20of%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20began%20after%20authorities%20found%20babies%20being%20smuggled%20in%20biscuit%20boxes%20in%20Baduria%2C%20North%2024%20Parganas%20in%202016.%20This%20discovery%20led%20the%20Central%20Adoption%20Resource%20Authority%20(CARA)%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20CID%20in%20January%202017.%20The%20complaint%20pointed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cirregularities%E2%80%9D%20at%20three%20homes%20run%20by%20Chandana%20Chakraborty%20in%20Jalpaiguri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20in%202016%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Government%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20in%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20Subodh%20Bhattacharya%2C%20raised%20another%20red%20flag.%20He%20accused%20an%20NGO%20official%20in%20Jalpaiguri%20of%20running%20a%20child%20trafficking%20operation%20disguised%20as%20a%20charitable%20organisation%2C%20and%20even%20alleged%20government%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20the%20CID%20to%20take%20over%20the%20investigation%20in%202017%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chakraborty%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Bimala%20Shishu%20Griha%20and%20Ashray%2C%20and%20her%20brother%20Manas%20Bhowmik.%20The%20Ashray%20Orphanage%20used%20forged%20documents%20and%20fake%20stamps%20and%20certificates%2C%20and%20had%20allegedly%20sold%20at%20least%20two%20dozen%20children.%20According%20to%20the%20CID%2C%20the%20cost%20for%20each%20child%20sold%20abroad%20ranged%20from%20Rs%20three%20to%20five%20lakh%2C%20while%20for%20those%20trafficked%20within%20India%2C%20the%20charges%20varied%20between%20Rs%20one%20and%20three%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20her%20interrogation%2C%20Chakraborty%20informed%20the%20CID%20that%20BJP%20leader%20Juhi%20Chowdhury%20accompanied%20her%20to%20Delhi%20to%20address%20the%20trafficking%20matter%20and%20held%20meetings%20with%20BJP%20leaders%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%20and%20Roopa%20Ganguly%2C%20who%20were%20later%20interrogated%20by%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChowdhury%20was%20arrested%20from%20near%20the%20Nepal%20border%2C%20following%20which%20the%20state%20BJP%20suspended%20her%20and%20her%20father%2C%20Rabindra%20Narayan%20Chowdhury%2C%20from%20the%20state%20committee.%20However%2C%20then%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Ganguly%20openly%20vouched%20for%20her%20innocence.%20BJP%20leader%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20also%20promised%20to%20provide%20her%20with%20legal%20help.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20CID%20questioned%20BJP%20national%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20West%20Bengal%20during%20that%20period.%20Vijayvargiya%20termed%20the%20questioning%20%E2%80%98political%20vendetta%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChowdhury%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20after%20her%20arrest.%20She%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20matter%20is%20sub%20judice.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakraborty%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Bhowmik%2C%20also%20out%20on%20bail%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20the%20case%20has%20gone%20off%20the%20radar%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Officially%20though%2C%20the%20CID%20maintains%20that%20the%20Jalpaiguri%20child%20trafficking%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20close%20to%20the%20ruling%20parties%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20the%20state%20were%20running%20this%20racket.%20North%20Bengal%20is%20strategically%20located%20close%20to%20Nepal%2C%20Assam%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Jharkhand.%20The%20tea%20workers%20are%20in%20dire%20poverty.%20On%20the%20pretext%20of%20social%20activity%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20make%20huge%20money%20by%20trafficking%20or%20selling%20children%20in%20the%20name%20of%20adoption%2C%20using%20agents.%20They%20did%20not%20follow%20any%20laws%20related%20to%20adoption.%20A%20section%20of%20government%20officials%20were%20involved%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20CID%20official%20involved%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20also%20came%20under%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20in%202020%20both%20the%20National%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Commissions%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Flitigation%2Fsc-castigates-national-and-wb-child-rights-commissions-for-jurisdictional-tussle-in-jalpaiguri-trafficking-case%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Supreme%2520Court%2520criticised%2520the%2520National%2520and%2Cjurisdiction%2520in%2520the%2520Jalpaiguri%2520child%2520trafficking%2520case.%5C%22%3Ewere%20castigated%20by%20the%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20losing%20sight%20of%20their%20primary%20duty%20to%20protect%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20case%20is%20a%20classic%20example%20where%20in%20the%20fight%20between%20the%20State%20Commission%20and%20the%20National%20Commission%20the%20children%20have%20been%2C%20all%20but%20forgotten.%20We%20are%20sorry%20that%20this%20Court%20has%20to%20spend%20its%20time%20resolving%20such%20disputes%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Deepak%20Gupta%20and%20Aniruddha%20Bose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Subodh%20Bhattacharya%2C%20the%20whistleblower%20un%20the%20case%2C%20was%20unceremoniously%20dropped%20from%20the%20Government%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government.%20In%202023%2C%20Subodh%20and%20his%20wife%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fwest-bengal%2Ftmc-youth-leader-in-jalpaiguri-sent-to-police-custody-in-abetment-to-suicide-case-2730001%5C%22%3Edied%20by%20suicide%2C%20leaving%20a%20note%20holding%20Trinamool%20Youth%20Congress%20leader%20Saikat%20Chatterjee%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20three%20of%20his%20aides%20responsible%20for%20their%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20suicide%20note%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.casemine.com%2Fjudgement%2Fin%2F6492820bd52177035a08209f%5C%22%3Ethe%20couple%20alleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Subodh%20was%20harassed%20by%20Chatterjee%20for%20naming%20him%20in%20the%20child%20trafficking%20case.%20Subodh%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20had%20led%20to%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20seven%20individuals%2C%20including%20Chandana%20Chakraborty%2C%20the%20names%20of%20Chatterjee%20and%20three%20others%20were%20omitted%20by%20the%20CID.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Flawyer-s-glare-on-baby-sale%2Fcid%2F1525852%5C%22%3EChatterjee%20used%20to%20work%20as%20Chakraborty%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reportedly%20facilitated%2020%20of%20the%2052%20adoptions%20from%20Chakraborty%E2%80%99s%20shelter%20homes%2C%20but%20later%20claimed%20to%20have%20disassociated%20himself%20after%20coming%20to%20know%20of%20the%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChatterjee%20surrendered%20to%20the%20police%20in%20October%202023%2C%20following%20the%20dismissal%20of%20his%20anticipatory%20bail%20plea%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20but%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20soon%20after.%20His%20anticipatory%20bail%20petition%20at%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20in%20June%202023%20was%20handled%20by%20advocate%20Kishore%20Dutta%2C%20who%20became%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20advocate%20general%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Bengali%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709798410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2F