g%2083%20were%20self-reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20not%20reported%20any%20vaccine-related%20side%20effects%2C%20and%20underwent%20repeated%20antigen%20and%20PCR%20testing%20for%2029%20months%2C%20revealing%20no%20evidence%20of%20a%20COVID-19%20infection.%20However%2C%20the%20researchers%20caution%20that%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20his%20Covid-free%20status%20can%20be%20attributed%20directly%20to%20his%20%E2%80%9Chypervaccination%E2%80%9D%20regimen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20actions%20turned%20him%20into%20a%20unique%20case%20study%2C%20offering%20insights%20into%20the%20effects%20of%20repeated%20vaccination%20against%20the%20same%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Researchers%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Emily%20Happy%20Miller%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20medicine%20and%20microbiology%20and%20immunology%20at%20Albert%20Einstein%20College%20of%20Medicine%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mce-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F06%2Fhealth%2Fcovid-217-shots-hypervaccination-lancet%2Findex.html%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F06%2Fhealth%2Fcovid-217-shots-hypervaccination-lancet%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20really%20unusual%20case%20of%20someone%20receiving%20that%20many%20Covid%20vaccines%2C%20clearly%20not%20following%20any%20type%20of%20guidelines.%26quot%3B%20She%20speculated%2C%20%26quot%3BPerhaps%20he%20didn't%20get%20Covid%20because%20he%20was%20well-protected%20in%20the%20first%20three%20doses%20of%20the%20vaccine.%20We%20also%20don't%20know%20anything%20about%20his%20behaviours.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20author%20of%20the%20study%2C%20Dr%20Kilian%20Schober%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20Friedrich-Alexander%20University%20Erlangen-N%C3%BCrnberg%2C%20highlighted%20the%20individual%20nature%20of%20this%20case%20study%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20results%20could%20not%20be%20generalised.%20He%20underlined%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20benefit%20is%20not%20much%20bigger%20if%20you%20get%20vaccinated%20three%20times%20or%20200%20times.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEffects%20of%20Hypervaccination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20learning%20about%20the%20man%20through%20news%20reports%2C%20researchers%20at%20The%20Lancet%20contacted%20him%20in%20May%202022%20via%20the%20prosecutor%20handling%20his%20case%2C%20when%20he%20had%20already%20received%20213%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20cautioned%20by%20the%20researchers%20against%20further%20vaccinations%2C%20he%20agreed%20to%20provide%20medical%20information%2C%20blood%2C%20and%20saliva%20samples.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20he%20received%20an%20additional%20four%20Covid%20shots%2C%20bringing%20his%20total%20to%20217.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20willingly%20gave%20blood%20and%20saliva%20samples%20for%20the%20researchers%C2%A0to%20study.%20They%20compared%20his%20antibody%20levels%20with%2029%20people%20who%20got%20three%20mRNA%20COVID-19%20shots.%20After%20his%20214th%20and%20215th%20shots%2C%20his%20antibody%20levels%20peaked%2C%20mirroring%20the%20control%20group's%20response.%20The%20217th%20shot%20resulted%20in%20a%20modest%20increase.%20Despite%20the%20extreme%20number%20of%20doses%2C%20the%20man%20did%20not%20experience%20significant%20side%20effects%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20researchers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20summary%2C%20our%20case%20report%20shows%20that%20SARS-CoV-2%20hypervaccination%20did%20not%20lead%20to%20adverse%20events%20and%20increased%20the%20quantity%20of%20spike-specific%20antibodies%20and%20T%20cells%20without%20having%20a%20strong%20positive%20or%20negative%20effect%20on%20the%20intrinsic%20quality%20of%20adaptive%20immune%20responses%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mce-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flaninf%2Farticle%2FPIIS1473-3099(24)00134-8%2Ffulltext%23%2520%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flaninf%2Farticle%2FPIIS1473-3099(24)00134-8%2Ffulltext%23%2520%5C%22%3Ethe%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0reads.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20found%20no%20signs%20of%20SARS-CoV-2%20breakthrough%20infections%20in%20%5Bthe%20man%5D%20to%20date%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20clarified%20whether%20this%20is%20causally%20related%20to%20the%20hypervaccination%20regimen.%20Importantly%2C%20we%20do%20not%20endorse%20hypervaccination%20as%20a%20strategy%20to%20enhance%20adaptive%20immunity%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20examined%20various%20markers%20to%20assess%20the%20functioning%20of%20his%20adaptive%20immune%20system%2C%20which%20includes%20T%20cells%20and%20B%20cells%20-%20the%20two%20main%20cell%20types%20in%20this%20system.%20Contrary%20to%20concerns%20that%20frequent%20exposure%20to%20the%20virus%20through%20hypervaccination%20might%20lead%20to%20immune%20fatigue%2C%20the%20study%20found%20that%20in%20this%20case%2C%20hypervaccination%20increased%20the%20quantity%20of%20T%20cells%20and%20B%20cell%20products%20without%20compromising%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20adaptive%20immune%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20Dr%20Kilian%20Schober%20explained%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mce-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fau.eu%2F2024%2F03%2F05%2Fnews%2Fresearch%2Fresearchers-investigate-immune-response-of-a-man-who-received-217-covid-vaccinations%2F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fau.eu%2F2024%2F03%2F05%2Fnews%2Fresearch%2Fresearchers-investigate-immune-response-of-a-man-who-received-217-covid-vaccinations%2F%5C%22%3Enews%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20take%20the%20allegory%20of%20the%20immune%20system%20as%20an%20army%2C%20the%20number%20of%20soldiers%20is%20higher%2C%20but%20the%20soldiers%20themselves%20are%20not%20different...The%20observation%20that%20no%20noticeable%20side%20effects%20were%20triggered%20in%20spite%20of%20this%20extraordinary%20hypervaccination%20indicates%20that%20the%20drugs%20have%20a%20good%20degree%20of%20tolerability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709796600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2Fr6e5kmv8_vaccine-generic-650_625x300_25_June_21.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhat-experts-said-on-man-who-took-217-covid-shots-on-purpose-5192319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2062-year-old%20man%20from%20Germany%20intentionally%20got%20217%20doses%20of%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20over%2029%20months.%20The%20vaccinations%20were%20not%20part%20of%20any%20clinical%20study%20and%20were%20administered%20for%20what%20the%20man%20claims%20were%20%26quot%3Bprivate%20reasons.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhat-experts-said-on-man-who-took-217-covid-shots-on-purpose-5192319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhat-experts-said-on-man-who-took-217-covid-shots-on-purpose-5192319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhat-experts-said-on-man-who-took-217-covid-shots-on-purpose-5192319%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Timoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%20Eyes%20%E2%80%98Musical%20Cinematic%20Universe%E2%80%99%20With%20His%20Bob%20Dylan%20and%20Austin%20Butler%E2%80%99s%20Elvis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709796304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fchalamet-elvis-split.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235932936%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Timoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%20is%20ready%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20MCU%3A%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmusical%20cinematic%20universe.%E2%80%9D%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20NME%20while%20promoting%20%E2%80%9CDune%3A%20Part%20Two%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chalamet%20said%20he%20wants%20Austin%20Butler%E2%80%99s%20Elvis%20to%20appear%20in%2