%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-why-bjp-candidate-pawan-singh-in-west-bengals-asansol-dropped-out-rajnath-singh-says-5192586%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Was%20Minister%20In%20Vajpayee%20Era...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rajnath%20Singh%20On%20What's%20Different%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20stature%20in%20international%20forums%20has%20grown%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20today%20while%20comparing%20his%20experiences%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20and%20the%20current%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%20at%20NDTV's%20maiden%20defence%20summit%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20India's%20defence%20sector%20has%20become%20strong%20because%20the%20government%20has%20tried%20to%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3BIndianness%26quot%3B%20too.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20strengthened%20the%20defence%20sector%20from%20an%20India%20perspective.%20The%20result%20is%20India's%20rise%20on%20the%20international%20stage.%20The%20day%20is%20not%20far%20off%20when%20India%20will%20not%20only%20become%20a%20developed%20nation%2C%20but%20our%20military%20strength%20will%20be%20the%20greatest%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20his%20experience%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%2C%20the%20Defence%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20too.%20When%20I%20travelled%20to%20other%20countries%20and%20spoke%20on%20international%20forums%2C%20I%20felt%20our%20words%20were%20not%20taken%20very%20seriously.%20But%20when%20we%20speak%20on%20international%20forums%20now%2C%20the%20world%20takes%20note.%20This%20is%20how%20our%20stature%20has%20grown%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20prioritised%20the%20defence%20sector%20and%20encouraged%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20we%20put%20defence%20sector%20as%20our%20main%20priority.%20Atmanirbharta%20(self-reliance)%20was%20encouraged%20and%20we%20introduced%20many%20Make-in-India%20initiatives.%20Our%20focus%20was%20on%20military%20modernisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20saying%20that%20previous%20governments%20did%20not%20put%20emphasis%20on%20defence%20sector.%20But%20we%20brought%20atmanirbharta%20in%20the%20defence%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20India%20now%20imports%20technology%20%26quot%3Bonly%20when%20our%20own%20innovation%20falls%20short%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20government's%20vision%20to%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20other%20countries%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20nation%2C%20adopting%20a%20mindset%20of%20technological%20dependence%20on%20other%20countries%20can%20be%20detrimental%20to%20our%20overall%20well-being%2C%20impacting%20various%20facets%20such%20as%20literature%2C%20daily%20life%20and%20every%20aspect%20of%20our%20existence.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20striving%20to%20break%20free%20from%20this%20mentality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709795280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fcjp9c2co_rajnath-singh-ndtv-summit_625x300_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-ndtv-defence-summit-i-was-minister-in-vajpayee-era-rajnath-singh-on-whats-different-now-5192427%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20stature%20in%20international%20forums%20has%20grown%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20today%20while%20comparing%20his%20experiences%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20and%2