%20sector%20as%20our%20main%20priority.%20Atmanirbharta%20(self-reliance)%20was%20encouraged%20and%20we%20introduced%20many%20Make-in-India%20initiatives.%20Our%20focus%20was%20on%20military%20modernisation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhether%20from%20land%2C%20air%20or%20sea%2C%20if%20anyone%20attacks%20India%2C%20our%20forces%20will%20respond%20with%20great%20force.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20war%20at%20all%20times%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20peacetime%20or%20not.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20ready.%20We%20have%20never%20occupied%20anyone's%20land.%20But%20if%20anyone%20attacks%20India%2C%20we%20are%20in%20such%20a%20position%20that%20we%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20reply.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20am%20not%20saying%20that%20previous%20governments%20did%20not%20put%20emphasis%20on%20the%20defence%20sector.%20But%20we%20brought%20atmanirbharta%20in%20the%20defence%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20must%20break%20free%20from%20thinking%20that%20we%20are%20dependent%20on%20others%20and%20change%20the%20way%20we%20approach%20progress.%20Those%20whose%20feet%20are%20weak%20and%20defeated%20should%20follow%20the%20trodden%20path%2C%20we%20like%20the%20path%20created%20by%20our%20journey.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20strengthened%20the%20defence%20sector%20from%20an%20India%20perspective.%20The%20result%20is%20India's%20rise%20on%20the%20international%20stage.%20The%20day%20is%20not%20far%20off%20when%20India%20will%20not%20only%20become%20a%20developed%20nation%2C%20but%20our%20military%20strength%20will%20be%20the%20greatest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20too.%20When%20I%20travelled%20to%20other%20countries%20and%20spoke%20on%20international%20forums%2C%20I%20felt%20our%20words%20were%20not%20taken%20very%20seriously.%20But%20when%20we%20speak%20on%20international%20forums%20now%2C%20the%20world%20takes%20note.%20This%20is%20how%20our%20stature%20has%20grown.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709793840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F535apd98_rajnath-singh-ndtv-defence-summit-_625x300_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-defence-summit-ready-for-war-at-all-times-rajnath-singhs-top-quotes-at-ndtv-summit-5192474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20today%20that%20if%20anyone%20attacks%20India%2C%20armed%20forces%20are%20perfectly%20equipped%20to%20respond%20swiftly%20and%20efficiently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-defence-summit-ready-for-war-at-all-times-rajnath-singhs-top-quotes-at-ndtv-summit-5192474%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-defence-summit-ready-for-war-at-all-times-rajnath-singhs-top-quotes-at-ndtv-summit-5192474%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-defence-summit-ready-for-war-at-all-times-rajnath-singhs-top-quotes-at-ndtv-summit-5192474%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SingTel%20sells%200.8%25%20stake%20in%20Bharti%20Airtel%20for%20%24711%20mn%20to%20GQG%20Partners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709793536000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-09%2F01%2Ffull%2F1630436084-3893.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsingtel-sells-0-8-stake-in-bharti-airtel-for-711-million-to-gqg-partners-124030700199_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Post%20the%20transaction%2C%20SingTel%20will%20hold%20an%20effective%20stake%20of%2029%20per%20cent%20in%20Airtel%2C%20which%20would%20be%20valued%20at%20around%20S%2433%20billion%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcom