ted%20the%20car%20to%20be%20fully%20autonomous%2C%20so%20the%20controller%20was%20for%20situations%20when%20the%20vehicle%20got%20stuck%20in%20situations%20that%20were%20particularly%20difficult%20to%20navigate%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20whether%20this%20version%20of%20the%20Apple%20car%20would%20have%20shipped.%20The%20tech%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-is-shutting-down-its-ev-project-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Editched%20its%20plans%20for%20the%20ambitious%20EV%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%2027%2C%20after%20almost%2010%20years%20of%20work%20under%20a%20secretive%20%26quot%3BProject%20Titan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg's%20in-depth%20feature%20on%20the%20project%20detailed%20how%20the%20team%20cycled%20through%20various%20designs%2C%20including%20one%20after%20the%20%26quot%3BBread%20Loaf%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20internally%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BI-Beam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BBread%20Loaf%2C%26quot%3B%20however%2C%20deeply%20impressed%20Cook%20and%20other%20Apple%20executives%2C%20who%20after%20trying%20out%20the%20car%20wanted%20it%20to%20to%20have%20the%20most%20sophisticated%20self-driving%20software%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20tech%20that%20Apple%20engineers%20weren't%20confident%20they%20could%20achieve%20at%20the%20time%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20changed%20tack%20at%20least%20once%20on%20this%20strategy%2C%20opting%20to%20move%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-car-ev-autonomous-level-two-design-delays-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELevel%202%20autonomous%20driving%20in%20January%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20drivers%20to%20take%20their%20hands%20off%20the%20wheel%20temporarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20Apple's%20original%20ambition%20for%20its%20car.%20The%20firm%20hoped%20that%20the%20EV%20would%20navigate%20independently%20without