ws%2Fbengaluru-bengaluru-water-crisis-man-claims-wet-wipes-being-used-in-crisis-hit-bengaluru-internet-reacts-5186168%5C%22%3Ewater%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20exploring%20alternative%20solutions%2C%20including%20recycled%20and%20treated%20water%20from%20residents'%20associations.%20Helplines%20are%20overwhelmed%20as%20the%20city%20faces%20a%20shortfall%20of%20over%201%2C500%20MLD%20(Million%20Liters%20Per%20Day)%20in%20its%20daily%20water%20requirement%2C%20which%20ranges%20between%202%2C600%20MLD%20to%202%2C800%20MLD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20has%20taken%20a%20political%20turn%2C%20with%20leaders%20of%20the%20opposition%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20the%20government%20for%20its%20alleged%20failure%20to%20implement%20effective%20water%20management%20measures.%20The%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20issued%20a%20stern%20warning%2C%20threatening%20protests%20if%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20does%20not%20take%20decisive%20action%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20has%20responded%20by%20announcing%20the%20establishment%20of%20control%20rooms%20and%20dedicated%20helpline%20numbers.%20Task%20forces%2C%20headed%20by%20local%20MLAs%2C%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20address%20the%20drought%20situation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20223%20Taluks%20out%20of%20236%20that%20have%20been%20declared%20drought-hit%2C%20with%20219%20facing%20severe%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20assured%20the%20public%20that%20the%20government%20would%20spare%20no%20effort%20in%20tackling%20the%20water%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20tankers%20has%20risen%20steadily%2C%20escalating%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%2C500%2C%20and%20recently%20peaking%20at%20Rs%202%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20anticipation%20of%20a%20more%20severe%20summer%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20estimates%207%2C082%20villages%20across%20Karnataka%2C%20along%20with%201%2C193%20wards%2C%20including%20those%20in%20Bengaluru%20Urban%20district%2C%20face%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20drinking%20water%20crisis%20in%20the%20upcoming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20revenue%20department%2C%20Tumakuru%20district%20tops%20the%20list%20with%20746%20vulnerable%20villages%2C%20while%20Uttara%20Kannada%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20vulnerable%20wards.%20Bengaluru%20Urban%20district%20is%20not%20exempt%2C%20with%20174%20villages%20and%20120%20wards%20identified%20as%20susceptible%20to%20the%20impending%20water%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20exploring%20various%20options%20to%20mitigate%20the%20crisis%2C%20including%20regulating%20water%20tankers%20and%20considering%20the%20use%20of%20treated%20water%20from%20apartment%20complexes%20for%20non-portable%20purposes.%20In%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20water%20is%20supplied%20through%20120%20municipal%20tankers%20and%20232%20water%20board%20tankers%2C%20the%20situation%20remains%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWater%20Tanker%20Rates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengaluru%20city%20administration%20took%20action%20against%20the%20illicit%20water%20tanker%20operations.%20Responding%20to%20the%20Bangalore%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB)%20plea%20to%20standardise%20water%20rates%2C%20and%20in%20light%20of%20the%20escalating%20demands%20and%20surging%20prices%20for%20tanker%20services%2C%20the%20District%20Collector%20of%20Bangalore%20City%2C%20established%20rates%20for%20200%20privately%20operated%20tankers%20over%20a%20four-month%20duration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20200%20private%20tankers%20are%20engaged%20on%20a%20contractual%20basis%20to%20deliver%20water%20to%20Bangalore%20city.%20The%20rates%2C%20determined%20by%20Bengaluru%20City%20District%20Collector%20KA%20Dayananda%2C%20are%20outlined%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERates%20for%20tankers%20within%20a%205%20km%20radius%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERs%20600%20for%20a%206%2C000-litre%20water%20tanker%20within%205%20km.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%20700%20for%20an%208%2C000-litre%20water%20tanker.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%201000%20for%20a%2012%2C000-litre%20water%20tanker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20distances%20beyond%205%20km%20but%20within%2010%20km%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERs%20750%20for%20a%206%2C000-liter%20water%20tanker.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%20850%20for%20an%208%2C000-litre%20water%20tanker.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%201200%20for%20a%2012%2C000-litre%20water%20tanker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20rates%20are%20inclusive%20of%20GST.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709788560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F28kb6afo_bengaluru-water-crisis-_625x300_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-bengaluru-suffers-worst-ever-water-crisis-political-blame-game-begins-5192032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Water%20Crisis%3A%20As%20Bengaluru%20grapples%20with%20an%20unprecedented%20water%20crisis%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20exploring%20alternative%20solutions%2C%20including%20recycled%20and%20treated%20water%20from%20residents'%20associations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-bengaluru-suffers-worst-ever-water-crisis-political-blame-game-begins-5192032%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-bengaluru-suffers-worst-ever-water-crisis-political-blame-game-begins-5192032%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-bengaluru-suffers-worst-ever-water-crisis-political-blame-game-begins-5192032%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22State's%20Right%20to%20Approach%20SC%2C%20Union%20Can't%20Ask%20Kerala%20to%20Withdraw%20Suit%3A%20Bench%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%206)%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20state%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20right%2C%20under%20Article%20131%2C%20to%20file%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20and%20so%20the%20Centre%20was%20wrong%20to%20say%20it%20would%20accept%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20request%20for%20additional%20borrowing%20only%20if%20it%20withdraws%20its%20suit%20filed%20in%20the%20apex%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20K.V.%20Viswanathan%20was%20hearing%20the%20plea%20filed%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%20against%20borrowing%20limits%20for%20states%20imposed%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20On%20the%20previous%20hearing%20date%2C%20the%20bench%20was%20told%20that%20the%20Union%20had%20allowed%20Rs%2013%2C%20608%20crore%20additional%20borrowing%2C%20but%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20the%20state%20withdraw%20its%20petition%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-asks-centre-to-not-insist-that-kerala-should-withdraw-suit-to-allow-additional-borrowing-251420%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20judges%20asked%20how%20a%20condition%20like%20this%20could%20be%20placed%2C%20since%20it%20is%20a%20state%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20approach%20the%20apex%20court.%20%E2%80%9COne%20condition%20was%20that%20the%20demand%20can%20be%20considered%20only%20after%20the%20disposal%20or%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20suit.%20We%20are%20saying%2C%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20you%20can%20insist%20for%20acceptance%20of%20other%20conditions%E2%80%A6but%20what%20we%20only%20want%20to%20suggest%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20insist%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20suit.%20Rest%20of%20the%20conditions%2C%20we%20understand%20your%20concerns%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Kant%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20ad-hoc%2C%20provisional%2C%20interim%20arrangement%2C%20and%20to%20provide%20sufficient%20space%E2%80%A6to%20bail%20out%20them%20from%20the%20crisis%20they%20perceive%2C%20all%20other%20conditions%20you%20are%20entitled%20to%20insist%20on%20except%20the%20condition%20of%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20suit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWould%20you%20be%20able%20to%20say%20this%20to%20an%20individual%20litigant%3F%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20withdraw%20the%20suit.%20It%20is%20a%20constitutional%20right%20under%20Article%20131%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Viswanathan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20would%20not%20pass%20any%20orders%20for%20the%20moment%2C%20and%20the%20state%20and%20Union%20governments%20should%20hold%20a%20meeting%20to%20try%20and%20sort%20the%20matter%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHold%20a%20meeting%2C%20take%20this%2013%2C608%2C%20make%20out%20a%20case%20for%20the%20remaining%2C%20except%20for%20the%20condition%20of%20withdrawal%20of%20suit%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Justice%20Kant%20told%20both%20the%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20do%20one%20thing.%20Rs%2013%2C%20608%20crores%2C%20you%20(Union)%20yourself%20will%20do.%20We%20aren%E2%80%99t%20passing%20any%20order.%20As%20regards%20additional%20demand%2C%20a%20meeting%20be%20held%2C%20either%20today%20or%20tomorrow.%20And%20if%20you%20find%2C%20some%20additional%20amount%20can%20be%20released%2C%20subject%20to%20whatever%20conditions%20permissible%20as%20per%20Constitution%20except%20the%20condition%20for%20withdrawal%20of%20suit%2C%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Justice%20Kant%20told%20the%20AG%20and%20the%20ASG.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709788163000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fstates-right-to-approach-sc-union-cant-ask-kerala-to-withdraw-suit-bench%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bench%20had%20earlier%20been%20told%20that%20the%20Union%20had%20allowed%20Rs%2013%2C%20608%20crore%20additional%20borrowing%20for%20Kerala%2C%20but%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20the%20state%20withdraw%20its%20petition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fstates-right-to-approach-sc-union-cant-ask-kerala-to-withdraw-suit-bench%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple's%20car%20prototype%20was%20internally%20called%20the%20'Bread%20Loaf'%20because%20of%20its%20shape%3A%20Bloomberg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20wears%20sunglasses%20and%20smiles%20as%20he%20attends%20a%20sports%20game.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e93985ce7f1785b2e737e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20was%20reportedly%20impressed%20by%20the%20Apple%20car%20demonstration%2C%20though%20it%20was%20highly%20scripted%20and%20not%20representative%20of%20the%20technology%20his%20team%20had%20on%20hand%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Chang%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20employees%20called%20the%20design%20of%20their%20first%20electric%20vehicle%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3BBread%20Loaf%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20minivan%20was%20tested%20in%202020%20by%20executives%20as%20part%20of%20Apple's%20secret%C2%A0%26quot%3BProject%20Titan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Tim%20Cook%20appeared%20impressed%2C%20but%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3BBread%20Loaf%26quot%3B%20wasn't%20always%20viewed%20in%20a%20positive%20light%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20employees%20working%20on%20the%20tech%20giant's%20first%20electric%20car%20built%20a%20prototype%20in%202020%20that%20they%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BBread%20Loaf%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20name%20that%20was%20at%20times%20used%20disparagingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20moniker%20was%20reported%20in%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2024-03-06%2Fapple-car-s-crash-design-details-tim-cook-s-indecision-failed-tesla-deal%3FleadSource%3Dreddit_wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Bloomberg%20feature%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20secretive%20%26quot%3BProject%20Titan%26quot%3B%20to%20build%20Apple's%20failed%20car%2C%20which%20top%20executives%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-is-shutting-down-its-ev-project-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficially%20shelved%20on%20February%2027%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20nearly%20a%20decade%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-seater%20prototype%20resembled%20a%20minivan%20featuring%2C%20as%20Bloomberg%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3Brounded%20sides%2C%20an%20all-glass%20roof%2C%20sliding%20doors%2C%20and%20whitewall%20tires.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20team%20used%20the%20%26quot%3BBread%20Loaf%26quot%3B%20name%20%26quot%3Bnot%20always%20affectionally%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%20reporters%20Mark%20Gurman%20and%20Drake%20Bennett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20design%20would%20later%20change%20as%20the%20project's%20lead%20moved%20to%20another%20company%2C%20but%20the%20%26quot%3BBread%20Loaf%26quot%3B%20was%20an%20iteration%20that%20made%20it%20to%20the%20test%20tracks%20in%202020%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20took%20part%20in%20that%20demo%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20in%20what%20seems%20like%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20how%20trying%20to%20impress%20your%20boss%20can%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20the%20Appl