E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20even%20the%20army%2C%20presumed%20as%20secure%20employment%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20left%20untouched%20by%20the%20larger%20trends%20pointing%20to%20an%20economy%20dominantly%20characterised%20by%20increased%20informalisation%20of%20jobs%20which%20in%20some%20estimates%20is%20a%20whopping%2090.7%25%20of%20total%20employment.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20hire%20soldiers%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2022%2F6%2F20%2Fwe-have-been-cheated-indias-youth-reject-new-army-jobs-scheme%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20four-year%20contracts%20marked%20widespread%20protests%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcse.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FMehrotra_Parida_India_Employment_Crisis.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EScholar%20Santosh%20Mehrotra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20while%20analysing%20India%E2%80%99s%20employment%20crisis%2C%20notes%20that%20since%202012%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20increased%20share%20of%20informal%20jobs%20with%20less%20than%20one%20year%E2%80%99s%20contract%2C%20even%20in%20the%20government%20and%20public%20sector%20which%20has%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20disheartened%20labour%20force%20and%20educated%20but%20unemployed%20youth.%C2%A0%20Aspirations%20in%20young%20people%20for%20jobs%20in%20the%20public%20sector%20have%20remained%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20contraction%20of%20public%20sector%20employment%20since%20the%201990%E2%80%99s%20opening%20up%20of%20the%20economy.%20This%20marks%20a%20sea%20divide%20between%20lived%20experience%20of%20young%20people%20and%20the%20narratives%20peddled%20by%20the%20government%20leading%20to%20large-scale%20resentment%20and%20anger%20in%20young%20people%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20on%20his%20birthday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-gives-skilling-reskilling-upskilling-mantra-to-youth-11663413786604.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaddressed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2040%20lakh%20students%20of%20ITIs%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20their%20mantra%20should%20be%20skilling%2C%20reskilling%20and%20upskilling.%20Modi%20declared%20that%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20years%20more%20than%20four%20lakh%20seats%20have%20been%20added%20in%20ITIs%20and%20new%20opportunities%20and%20jobs%20are%20being%20created%20for%20the%20students%2C%20while%20completely%20glossing%20over%20the%20lived%20reality%20of%20unemployment%20that%20the%20students%20are%20grappling%20with.%20In%20the%20same%20beguiling%20spirit%2C%20recently%2C%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Funemployment-rate-india-lowest-level-6-years-pm-modi-8979775%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKaushal%20Deekshant%20Samaroh%20of%20the%20MSDE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20PM%20Modi%20noted%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20rate%20is%20lowest%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20last%20six%20years%20which%20was%20a%20result%20of%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20special%20focus%20on%20skill%20development%2C%20making%20skill%20development%20the%20indisputable%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20of%20unemployment.%20But%20the%20figure%20sta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ends%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-11-01%2Findia-jobless-rate-rises-to-more-than-two-year-high-cmie-says%3FleadSource%3Duverify%2520wall%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20by%20CMIE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20states%20that%20it%20rose%20to%2010.05%25%20in%20October%202023%2C%20the%20highest%20in%20more%20than%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYoung%20people%20in%20Assam%20tell%20us%20that%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpragnews.com%2Fregional%2Ftwelve-lakhs-applicants-for-twenty-six-thousands-assam-direct-recruitment-posts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20vacancies%20of%2026%2C000%20grade%203%20and%20grade%204%20posts%20were%20declared%20but%20over%2012%20lakh%20students%20appeared%20for%20the%20written%20exam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%20lament%20corruption%20in%20the%20system.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fguwahati%2Fapsc-scam-govt-initiates-action-against-34-officers%2Farticleshow%2F105110269.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Assam%20Public%20service%20commission%20jobs-for-cash%20scam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20they%20note%20how%20when%20a%20young%20person%20posted%20about%20this%20on%20social%20media%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20and%20jailed.%20This%20anger%20was%20mirrored%20in%20the%20protests%20that%20erupted%20as%20well.%20In%202022%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fbihar%2Fstory%2Fexplained-bihar-students-protesting-against-railways-train-set-on-fire-rrb-1905105-2022-01-27%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20several%20students%20in%20Bihar%20set%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20train%20on%20fire%20disrupting%20railway%20services%20protesting%20against%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20railway%20exams.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELand%20and%20livelihoods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20resource-rich%20state%20like%20Assam%2C%20in%20Odisha%20people%20lose%20land%20for%20state%20interests%20and%20with%20it%2C%20their%20livelihoods.%20The%20poor%20are%20displaced%20from%20their%20lands%2C%20and%20the%20poor%20are%20called%20on%20in%20a%20declining%20employment%20scenario%20in%20the%20country%20to%20protect%20corporate%20interests%20to%20join%20the%20police%20and%20the%20army.%20It%20is%2C%20curiously%2C%20also%20resource%20conservation%20efforts%20that%20displace%20people%20from%20their%20livelihoods.%20In%20Chilika%20Lake%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20fisherfolk%20who%20rely%20on%20fishing%20for%20a%20living%20lament%20on%20how%20the%20no-fishing%20boundary%20implemented%20by%20the%20state%20leaves%20them%20high%20and%20dry%20with%20declining%20community%20access%20to%20the%20lake.%20This%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20expansion%20of%20commercial%20aquaculture%2C%20puts%20traditional%20fisher%20folk%20in%20peril.%20They%20imagine%20they%20will%20have%20to%20move%20to%20daily%20wage%20labour%2C%20letting%20go%20of%20their%20age-old%20livelihood%20practice.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20them%20already%20work%20in%20a%20nearby%20factory%20for%20a%20paltry%20wage.%20They%20look%20towards%20the%20ITIs%20for%20the%20skills%20their%20children%20would%20require%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20the%20industries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07084729%2F30666486884_d05e1da86d_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07084729%2F30666486884_d05e1da86d_c.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07084729%2F30666486884_d05e1da86d_c-300x169.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700511%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20ILO%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%20DEED)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20youth%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Dediapada%20of%20Gujarat%20are%20dependent%20on%20the%20middlemen%20who%20take%20them%20as%20contractual%20labour%20for%20a%20few%20months%20in%20a%20year.%20The%20villagers%2C%20predominantly%20Adivasi%2C%20have%20no%20viable%20livelihood%20options%20other%20than%20cultivation.%20The%20elder%20of%20the%20village%20points%20towards%20a%2023-year-old%20boy%20who%20had%20done%20the%20fitter%20course%20in%20one%20of%20the%20ITIs%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20is%20now%20back%20to%20the%20village%20without%20a%20steady%20source%20of%20income.%20Even%20skilling%20himself%20has%20not%20amounted%20to%20a%20job%20and%20hence%20the%20elder%20concludes%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20cultivate%20their%20own%20land%20till%20the%20state%20does%20not%20usurp%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EUnder%20a%20constant%20threat%20of%20having%20their%20land%20taken%20away%20by%20the%20government%2C%20as%20happened%20to%20their%20kin%20because%20of%20the%20construction%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-sardar-patel-statue-of-unity-protests%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStatue%20of%20Unity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20few%20young%20people%20from%20the%20community%20do%20join%20the%20ITIs%20to%20secure%20a%20job.%20The%20rationale%20is%20that%20it%20will%20aid%20in%20building%20a%20better%20future%20for%20themselves%20if%20they%20do%20find%20their%20lands%20being%20taken%20away%20for%20such%20development%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EITIs%2C%20are%20responsible%20for%20providing%20vocational%20training%20of%20one%20to%20two%20years%20to%20the%20youth%20under%20their%20Craftsmen%20Training%20Scheme%20(CTS)%20with%20the%20objective%20that%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20steady%20flow%20of%20skilled%20labour%20to%20the%20industries%20and%20ensure%20reduction%20of%20unemployment%20for%20the%20educated%20youth.%20Currently%20standing%20at%2014%2C789%20(government%20and%20private)%20in%20number%20in%20the%20country%2C%20ITIs%20were%20established%20in%20the%201950s%20to%20provide%20skilled%20labour%20in%20large-scale%20manufacturing%20fuelled%20by%20the%20self-reliance%20ambitions%20of%20independent%20India.%20Several%20of%20these%20large-scale%20industrial%20projects%20involved%20displacing%20people%20from%20their%20lands%20but%20were%20called%20on%20to%20sacrifice%20for%20the%20good%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20promised%20jobs%20in%20these%20industries%20provided%20they%20trained%20in%20ITIs.%20Even%20today%2C%20in%202023%20when%20we%20ask%20people%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20there%20are%20third%20generations%20of%20a%20family%20who%20still%20go%20to%20ITIs%20so%20they%20can%20secure%20a%20job%20in%20these%20industries%20which%20had%20usurped%20their%20lands.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20mobility%20is%20still%20a%20dream%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20promise%20of%20structural%20transformation%20involving%20the%20moving%20of%20surplus%20labour%20of%20agriculture%20and%20informal%20activities%20to%20more%20productive%2C%20non-farm%20activities%20%E2%80%93%20which%20economists%20note%20as%20necessary%20for%20economic%20growth%20and%20for%20better%20employment%20%E2%80%93%20has%20not%20helped%20the%20lay%20person%20wishing%20for%20social%20mobility%20in%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20people%20are%20moving%20away%20from%20agriculture%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20move%20to%20informal%20activities%20than%20higher%20value%20secure%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkill%20issue%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EScholars%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2022%2F4%2Fspecial-articles%2Fmigration-skilling-and-employment-bengalurus-new.html%5C%22%3ECarol%20Upadhya%20and%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fauthor%2Fsupriya-roy-chowdhury%5C%22%3ESupriya%20Roy%20Chowdhury%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20note%20that%20after%201990%2C%20in%20the%20industrial%20stagnation%20accompanied%20by%20jobless%20growth%2C%20declining%20industrial%20jobs%20and%20increase%20in%20software%20services%2C%20ITIs%20saw%20trades%20change.%20Those%20related%20to%20hospitality%2C%20organised%20retail%2C%20housekeeping%2C%20security%20services%20and%20malls%20thus%20now%20mirrored%20the%20change%20the%20composition%20of%20jobs%20in%20the%20market%20as%20manufacturing%20jobs%20declined.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20unemployment%2C%20the%20central%20feature%20of%20the%20jobless%20growth%20and%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20population%20being%20under%20the%20age%20of%2025%2C%20scholars%2C%20economists%20and%20the%20government%20speak%20of%20how%20the%20demographic%20dividend%20should%20not%20turn%20into%20a%20demographic%20disaster.%20But%20by%202009%2C%20in%20a%20rebranding%20exercise%20absolving%20them%20of%20responsibility%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20state%20had%20framed%20the%20unemployment%20problem%20as%20a%20problem%20of%20inadequate%20skills%20of%20young%20people%20or%20more%20precisely%20that%20young%20people%20are%20unemployable%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20relevant%20skills.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Skill%20Policy%2C%202009%2C%20therefore%20introduced%20several%20changes%20to%20the%20skill%20landscape%20like%20introduction%20of%20short%20term%20vocational%20training%20courses%20%E2%80%93%20some%20lasting%20three%20months%20and%20target-based%20skilling%20with%20ambitious%20skilling%20targets%20setup%20for%20the%20state%20based%20on%20the%20count%20of%20young%20people%20skilled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20targets%20have%20since%20become%20a%20measure%20of%20success%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20now%20claims%20that%20a%20whopping%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fpolicy%2F1-1-cr-people-trained-21-4-lakh-placed-under-pmkvy-2-0-economic-survey%2Farticleshow%2F97498349.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E1.1%20crore%20people%20have%20been%20skilled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20under%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Kaushal%20Vikas%20Yojan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmodi-skill-india-stumbled%5C%22%3EHow%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Flagship%20Skill%20India%20Project%20Stumbled%20Hard%20in%20Its%20First%20Year%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20ruling%20government%20keeps%20iterating%20that%20they%20will%20propel%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy%20to%20the%20top%20position%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-promises-to-elevate-indias-economy-to-top-position-in-the-world%2Farticleshow%2F105059603.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eif%20elected%20for%20a%20third%20term%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20while%20congratulating%20themselves%20for%20already%20being%20at%20the%205th%20position%2C%20the%20perils%20of%20this%20goal%20are%20experienced%20by%20the%20marginalised%2C%20especially%20the%20youth.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%2C%20Rajiv%20Chandrashekhar%20recently%20put%20the%20onus%20of%20unemployment%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Funemployment-narrative-wrong-many-still-at-a-disadvantage-due-to-lack-of-skills-rajeev-chandrasekhar%2Farticleshow%2F101763011.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elack%20of%20skills%20in%20the%20youth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20he%20ascertained%20that%20there%20are%20many%20jobs%20available%20only%20that%20the%20young%20have%20no%20skill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20our%20interactions%20with%20the%20youth%20in%20many%20ITIs%2C%20when%20we%20asked%20them%20to%20imagine%20the%20possibilities%20for%20themselves%2020%20years%20from%20now%2C%20they%20hesitate%20and%20shy%20away%20from%20putting%20their%20thoughts%20on%20paper.%20Arnob%2C%20a%20student%20of%20diesel%20mechanic%20trade%20of%20ITI%20Tinsukia%20in%20Assam%20after%20staring%20into%20the%20sheet%20for%20a%20few%20long%20minutes%2C%20retorts%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20future%20is%20as%20bright%20as%20this%20sheet%20of%20paper.%20It%20is%20so%20bright%20that%20everything%20is%20blinded%20by%20it.%E2%80%9D%20All%20students%20laugh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20unison%20at%20his%20clever%20remark.%20Being%20the%20troublemaker%20of%20the%20classroom%20and%20the%20son%20of%20a%20government%20school%20teacher%2C%20Arnob%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20a%20job%2C%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20girlfriend%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20important.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20discussion%20turns%20serious%2C%20the%20youth%20try%20to%20figure%20out%20why%20it%20is%20that%20their%20state%20has%20no%20jobs.%20%E2%80%9CMaybe%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20Assam%20has%20been%20in%20turmoil%20in%20the%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20some%20say.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20buying%20into%20the%20state%20narrative%20of%20skill-deficit%2C%20many%20young%20people%20enrol%20in%20ITIs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eafter%20finishing%20masters%20degrees%20in%20geography%2C%20political%20science%2C%20or%20zoology%2C%20or%20technical%20degrees%20like%20bachelors%20in%20engineering%20or%20polytechnic.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20attached%20to%20the%20certificates%20of%20ITIs.%20They%20say%20practical%20knowledge%20is%20important%20which%20is%20what%20they%20get%20here%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20theoretical%20knowledge%20provided%20elsewhere.%20One%20of%20the%20students%20in%20ITI%20Jorhat%20in%20the%20fitter%20trade%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20vacancy%20for%20one%20engineer%20then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20vacancy%20for%20150%20fitters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20reiterate%20the%20dominant%20narrative%20that%20the%20academic%20college%20degrees%20give%20them%20theoretical%20knowledge%20which%20is%20of%20no%20use%20in%20the%20current%20modern%20world.%20And%20hence%20they%20come%20to%20ITIs%20as%20ITIs%20give%20them%20the%20relevant%20practical%20knowledge%20that%20will%20land%20them%20jobs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Halol%2C%20Sheetal%20tells%20us%20she%20is%20pursuing%20her%20BSc%20in%20correspondence%20while%20enrolled%20in%20the%20Computer%20Operator%20and%20Programming%20Assistant%20(COPA)%20trade%20in%20the%20ITI.%C2%A0%20In%20Dibrugarh%2C%20Pooja%20has%20completed%20midwife%20training%20and%20then%20trained%20as%20a%20nurse%20and%20then%20moved%20to%20ITI%20while%20really%20wanting%20to%20join%20the%20army.%20In%20Silchar%2C%20Aradhya%2C%20Kusum%20and%20Lavani%2C%20friends%20who%20worked%20in%20a%20private%20school%20have%20quit%20their%20low%20paying%20jobs%20to%20learn%20stenography%20which%20they%20tell%20us%20will%20fetch%20them%20better%20jobs.%20The%20age%20span%20of%20students%20in%20ITI%20institutions%20range%20anywhere%20between%2015%20to%2038.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07085149%2F24083848365_f5f794c540_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07085149%2F24083848365_f5f794c540_c.jpg%20799w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07085149%2F24083848365_f5f794c540_c-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700513%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Rajesh_India%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%20DEED)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20jobs%20to%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202014%2C%20the%20narrative%20has%20shifted%20from%20%E2%80%98jobs%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98entrepreneurship%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20instated%20a%20Ministry%20for%20Skill%20development%20and%20Entrepreneurship.%20The%20Skill%20India%20Mission%2C%20also%20launched%20in%202015%2C%20put%20an%20increased%20focus%20on%20entrepreneurship.%20This%20was%20reflected%20in%20policy%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Policy%20(2009)%20was%20replaced%20by%20National%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20Policy%20(2015)%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20new%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Funleashing-india-s-entrepreneurial-energy-398379%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Prime%20Minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20famously%20said%20India%20needs%20to%20become%20a%20nation%20of%20job%20givers%20rather%20than%20seekers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Mayurbhanj%2C%20from%20a%20tiny%20village%20all%20men%20have%20migrated%20for%20work%20to%20the%20industrial%20districts%20and%20only%20return%20for%20brief%20periods%20of%20time.%20The%20women%20who%20are%20left%20alone%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20house%2C%20kids%20and%20farmlands%20(for%20those%20who%20own%20it)%2C%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20tailoring%20courses%20under%20the%20short%20term%20vocational%20training%20programmes.%20The%20women%20laugh%20the%20course%20off.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20all%20open%20up%20tailoring%20shops%2C%20who%20will%20give%20us%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20ask.%20They%20point%20to%20the%20thoughtlessness%20of%20such%20programmes%20designed%20by%20the%20government%20which%20defy%20the%20basic%20demand-and-supply%20concepts%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20foster%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20students%20do%20have%20the%20circumstance%20to%20start%20their%20own%20business%20they%20recognise%20building%20capital%20is%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20need%20to%20do%2C%20which%20involves%20securing%20a%20job%20first.%20One%20student%20in%20ITI%20Jorhat%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20part-time%20rider%20in%20Rapido%20talks%20animatedly%20about%20his%20start-up%20idea.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20make%20an%20app%20for%20the%20youth%20of%20Assam%20where%20they%20can%20get%20part-time%20jobs%20like%20the%20ones%20we%20get%20in%20Rapido%20but%20with%20better%20pay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20only%20a%20job%20at%20ONGC%20can%20give%20him%20the%20funds%20necessary%20for%20such%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESelf-employment%2C%20many%20students%20know%2C%20needs%20considerable%20funds%20and%20the%20capacity%20to%20take%20risks%2C%20which%20at%20their%20position%20they%20do%20not%20have.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Scholar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1007%2F978-3-658-08502-5_5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKothanadaraman%20Kumar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20in%202016%20that%20only%2012%25%20students%20of%20government%20ITIs%20opt%20for%20self-employment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20disadvantages%2C%20tackling%20the%20government%20narrative%20of%20a%20skill%20deficit%20or%20opting%20for%20self-employment%20as%20a%20way%20out%20do%20not%20map%20the%20lived%20realities%20of%20young%20people%20and%20appear%20to%20be%20what%20may%20be%20called%20discursive%20narrative%20violence%20against%20the%20many%20ways%20young%20people%20struggle%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20student%20in%20ITI%20Talcher%20retrospectively%20speaks%20about%20how%20he%20decided%20to%20choose%20the%20fitter%20course.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20brother%20told%20me%20there%20are%20only%20two%20courses%20available%20in%20ITIs%2C%20one%20electrician%20and%20one%20fitter.%20If%20I%20want%20to%20make%20something%20I%20should%20go%20for%20fitter%20but%20if%20I%20want%20to%20control%20something%20through%20a%20computer%2C%20I%20should%20choose%20electrician.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Many%20students%2C%20like%20him%2C%20come%20to%20an%20ITI%20without%20prior%20and%20correct%20information%20only%20to%20realise%20the%20skills%20they%20are%20being%20provided%20might%20not%20be%20adequate%20for%20where%20they%20want%20to%20reach%20in%20life.%20Fitter%20and%20electrician%20trades%20are%20the%20top%20two%20trades%20in%20ITIs%20but%2071.57%25%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20fitter%20trade%20and%C2%A0%2064.81%25%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20electrician%20trade%20remain%20unoccupied%20as%20reported%20by%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fniti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-02%2FITI_Report_02022023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20NITI%20Aayog%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20students%20do%20not%20tell%20us%3Cspan%3E%20what%20kind%20of%20careers%20they%20see%20for%20themselves.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20do%20whatever%20opportunity%20is%20available.%E2%80%9D%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20that%20they%20are%20not%20passionate.%20The%20endless%20diversifying%20of%20their%20skillset%20is%20an%20act%20of%20agency%20and%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20participate%20in%20an%20unforgiving%20labour%20scenario%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShyam%2C%20a%20diesel%20mechanic%20student%20of%20ITI%20Majuli%2C%20is%20very%20passionate%20about%20geography.%20He%20finished%20a%20masters%20degree%20and%20wanted%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20PhD%20but%20life%20had%20different%20plans%20for%20him.%20Explaining%20animatedly%20how%20we%20can%20predict%20rains%20through%20clouds%2C%20he%20mentioned%20how%20he%20wanted%20to%20create%20change%20in%20his%20island%20through%20his%20expertise.%20But%20he%20is%20pursuing%20a%20diesel%20mechanic%20course.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENoting%20the%20dismal%20labour%20market%20%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcse.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in%2Fpublications%2Findias-employment-crisis-rising-education-levels-and-falling-non-agricultural-job-growth%2F%5C%22%3ESantosh%20M%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcse.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in%2Fpublications%2Findias-employment-crisis-rising-education-levels-and-falling-non-agricultural-job-growth%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eehrortra%2C%20based%20on%20his%20research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20shows%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ehow%20real%20wages%20have%20not%20increased%20for%20the%20youth%20even%20with%20increasing%20education%20levels%20which%20is%20felt%20acutely%20by%20the%20youth.%20Jean%20Dreze%20b%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eased%20on%20statistical%20estimates%20observes%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fagricultural-labour-unions-farming-progressive-futures-in-their-struggles%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOn%2520the%2520other%2520hand%252C%2520the%2Cagriculture%2520workers%252C%25200.3%2520percent).%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20growth%20rate%20of%20real%20wages%20between%202014-15%20and%202021-22%20was%20below%201%25%20per%20year%20%E2%80%93%200.9%25%2C%200.2%20%25%20and%200.3%25%C2%A0%20respectively%20for%20agricultural%20labour%2C%20construction%20workers%20and%20non-agricultural%20labour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESam%20Sonowal%2C%20a%20student%20in%20an%20ITI%20in%20Assam%2C%20expresses%20real%20fear%20that%20the%20struggles%20undertaken%20by%20his%20parents%20to%20put%20him%20through%20school%20and%20college%20may%20well%20be%20undone%20by%20his%20inability%20to%20get%20a%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20after%20enrolling%20in%20skilling%20institutions%2C%20students%20know%20securing%20a%20job%20is%20still%20difficult.%20An%20ITI%20student%20Adhin%20tells%20us%20that%20he%20knows%20of%20many%20who%20did%20not%20get%20a%20job%20after%20their%20course%20completed.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20others%20have%20joined%20Zomato%2C%20but%20they%20get%20little%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20a%20time%20of%20educated%20unemployment%20for%20many.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20have%20to%20leave%20my%20hometown%20for%20a%20job%20after%20I%20graduate.%20If%20I%20am%20closer%20home%20I%20can%20also%20work%20in%20the%20fields%20and%20stay%20home%2C%20reducing%20my%20expenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20student%20in%20an%20ITI%20in%20Gujarat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fi-xXV8TxwzU%3Fsi%3DDUnWo9MAxDfyulAq%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20and%20culture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20some%20extent%20the%20political%20economy%20and%20cultural%20politics%20of%20the%20state%20plays%20a%20role.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20a%20resource%20rich%20Assam%20where%20oil%2C%20petrochemicals%2C%20coal%20and%20tea%20production%20is%20huge%2C%20there%20is%20large%20capture%20of%20land%20and%20resources%20by%20corporates%20and%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20with%20very%20low%20employment%20generation.%20And%20even%20while%20it%20is%20extremely%20hard%20to%20get%20into%20these%20companies%20and%20recruitment%20is%20very%20low%2C%20scores%20of%20young%20people%20join%20ITIs%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20a%20job%20in%20the%20oil%20companies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20there%20are%20the%20cultural%20and%20social%20tensions%20that%20have%20gripped%20Assam%20on%20language%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20it%20which%20the%20students%20are%20very%20much%20aware%20of.%20Sunity%20in%20Silchar%20in%20Assam%20alleges%20that%20on%20a%20recent%20government%20recruitment%20drive%20the%20state%20didn%E2%80%99t%20recruit%20a%20single%20Bengali%20person.%20Unemployment%20can%20also%20make%20earlier%20tensions%20worse%20or%20foment%20new%20hatred%20between%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Gujarat%2C%20with%20its%20much-touted%20model%20of%20development%20with%20heavy%20industrialisation%20and%20tax%20havens%20to%20make%20it%20an%20investor%20friendly%20destination%20and%20relaxed%20labour%20laws%2C%20the%20challenges%20are%20different.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Dediapada%2C%20Adivasi%20students%20in%20the%20ITI%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20development%20is%20not%20for%20us%2C%20its%20for%20others%2C%20the%20other%20castes.%20Us%20Adivasis%20will%20always%20remain%20at%20the%20bottom%2C%20our%20lands%20and%20forests%20will%20be%20taken%20away%2C%20and%20we%20will%20have%20to%20scrounge%20for%20measly%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudents%20in%20the%20mining%20belts%20of%20Odisha%20hope%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20one%20of%20the%20mining%20companies%20even%20though%20they%20realise%20the%20destruction%20to%20human%20lives%20and%20the%20environment%20the%20mines%20have%20caused.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApprenticeship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlacement%2C%20many%20principals%20claim%2C%20is%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20ITIs.%C2%A0%20Most%20of%20the%20graduates%20do%20not%20prefer%20to%20travel%20too%20far%20for%20the%20job%20even%20when%20within%20the%20state.%20They%20lament%20the%20low%20wages%2C%20unable%20to%20sustain%20themselves.%20Unless%20you%20are%20placed%20in%20some%20well-paying%20industries%2C%20you%20only%20secure%20apprenticeship%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20job%20of%20ITI%20graduates%20%E2%80%93%20where%20they%20get%20a%20salary%20of%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%208000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20as%20initial%20salary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Apprenticeship%20Act%20was%20passed%20in%201961%20on%20the%20realisation%20that%20training%20in%20educational%20institutions%20is%20not%20sufficient%20for%20acquisition%20of%20skills%20and%20hence%2C%20students%20need%20to%20apprentice%20in%20industries%20to%20gain%20practical%20knowledge.%20Under%20the%20Act%2C%20the%20industries%20are%20mandated%20to%20pay%20the%20apprentices%20a%20minimum%20of%2070%25%20of%20minimum%20wage%20of%20the%20state%20where%20the%20industry%20is%20situated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20HR%20professional%20at%20an%20Assam%20factory%20reveals%20that%20bigger%20industries%20hire%20and%20fire%20apprentices%20constantly%20keeping%20them%20on%20company%20rolls%20for%20entry-level%20work%2C%20thus%20also%20reducing%20labour%20costs.%20When%20we%20ask%20him%20if%20his%20company%20hires%20apprentices%20after%20their%20apprentice%20period%2C%20he%20announces%20that%20they%20do.%20A%20little%20probing%20reveals%20how%20most%20apprentices%20are%20later%20hired%20as%20contract%20labour.%20Secure%20employment%20is%20reserved%20for%20only%20a%20few%20in%20the%20industry.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcse.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in%2Fpublications%2Findias-employment-crisis-rising-education-levels-and-falling-non-agricultural-job-growth%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMehrortra%20speaks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20how%20this%20is%20the%20dominant%20trend%20in%20the%20country%20with%20both%20government%20and%20private%20sectors%20where%20contract%20jobs%20with%20less%20than%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20contract%20are%20on%20the%20rise%20post%202011-12.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20like%20the%20government%20officials%20and%20the%20principals%20do%20not%20know%20that%20the%20apprenticeship%20stipend%20is%20unsustainable.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20ITI%20principal%20in%20Odisha%20tells%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CKids%20do%20not%20want%20to%20go%20to%20other%20districts%20or%20states%20because%20they%20will%20get%20Rs%2010%2C000-15%2C000%20there%2C%20in%20an%20unfamiliar%20place%2C%20which%20they%20can%20make%20doing%20daily%20wage%20labour%20closer%20to%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20foreman%20in%20an%20ITI%20in%20Gujarat%20comments%20on%20how%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eweak%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20young%20generation%20is%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20youth%20of%20today%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20work%20hard.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20simplicity%20and%20ease%20of%20these%20assumptions%20belie%20inherent%20contradictions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funemployment-rate-rose-to-10-09-percent-in-october-cmie-data%5C%22%3EUnemployment%20Rate%20Rose%20to%20Two-Year%20High%20of%2010.09%25%20in%20October%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20casteist%20roots%20of%20ITIs%20become%20more%20apparent%20when%20one%20understands%20the%20history%20behind%20it.%20A%20need%20for%20institutionalised%20forms%20of%20industrial%20education%20arose%20after%20the%201880s%20when%20the%20colonial%20state%20wanted%20to%20produce%20industry-oriented%20Indians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1177%2F0973174118810050%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Arun%20Kumar%20in%20his%20research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20points%20out%20that%20in%20colonial%20India%2C%20technical%20education%20was%20reserved%20for%20elites%20whereas%20industrial%20education%20was%20opening%20up%20for%20the%20masses.%20To%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20latter%2C%20the%20Lucknow%20Industrial%20School%20was%20opened%20in%201892%20as%20a%20collaborative%20effort%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20taluqdars.%20This%20school%20was%20thought%20to%20be%20ideal%20for%20low-caste%20artisans%20who%20had%20begun%20to%20demand%20education%20and%20for%20whom%20practical%20education%20fitted%20their%20aptitudes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20principal%20in%20an%20ITI%20in%20Gujarat%20who%20also%20told%20us%20that%20youngsters%20do%20not%20work%20hard%20speaks%20of%20how%20most%20employers%20of%20the%20industry%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98Patels%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20upper%20caste%20in%20Gujarat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20the%20state%20speaks%20of%20the%20need%20to%20raise%20aspirations%20of%20young%20people%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20it%20is%20the%20state%20which%20continues%20to%20limit%20the%20aspirations%20of%20students.%20Scholars%20such%20as%20Saraf%20have%20spoken%20of%20how%20by%20now%20introducing%20skilling%20programmes%20from%20secondary%20schools%20itself%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2016%2F18%2Fcommentary%2Fskill-training-or-nipping-potential-bud.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewill%20restrict%20young%20people%2C%20largely%20from%20soci%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eally%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%2C%20to%20low-productivity%20blue-collar%20employment%20in%20the%20informal%20sector%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20one%20of%20our%20industry%20visits%2C%20there%20was%20a%20clear%20demarcation%20of%20engineers%20and%20ITI%20graduates.%20There%20are%20separate%20uniforms%20that%20need%20to%20be%20worn%2C%20and%20most%20often%20engineering%20graduates%20are%20usually%20managers.%20If%20you%20are%20a%20blue-collar%20worker%20then%20your%20mobile%20is%20confiscated%20every%20morning%2C%20stored%20in%20blue%20boxes%20and%20returned%20to%20you%20when%20you%20finish%20your%20shift.%20And%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20boundaries%20between%20the%20blue%20collar%20worker%20and%20the%20white%20collar%20worker%20are%20rigid.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20country%20with%20a%20rigid%20caste%20system%2C%20decades%20of%20marginalisation%20is%20based%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20you%20do.%20The%20new%20claims%20on%20%E2%80%9Chardwork%E2%80%9D%20appear%20to%20perpetuate%20caste%20and%20class%20divisions%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Constantly%20shortchanged%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%E2%80%99s%20resolution%20that%20skilling%20will%20solve%20the%20unemployment%20crisis%20has%20led%20to%20counsellors%20going%20to%20the%20most%20remote%20villages%20to%20persuade%20young%20people%20from%20the%20most%20marginalised%20communities%20to%20join%20skilling%20institutes%20without%20thinking%20of%20contextual%20challenges.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20teacher%20in%20Odisha%20tells%20us%20that%20he%20has%20gone%20to%20Maoist-dominated%20areas%20to%20persuade%20young%20people%20to%20join%20the%20ITIs%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%20He%20says%20%E2%80%9CThese%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20value%20of%20this%20proposition%E2%80%9D.%20But%20in%20our%20conversations%20we%20see%20that%20the%20young%20people%20actually%20do%20see%20the%20value%20in%20such%20a%20proposition%2C%20only%20they%20do%20realise%20how%20they%20might%20be%20shortchanged.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20village%20in%20Kalahandi%20in%20Odisha%2C%20young%20girls%20tell%20us%20that%20an%20ITI%20teacher%20had%20come%20to%20their%20village%20and%20promised%20them%20scholarships%20and%20jobs%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20course%20if%20they%20join.%20They%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efought%20their%20parents%2C%20convinced%20them%20to%20let%20them%20join%20the%20ITI%20and%20finally%20enrolled.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20visibly%20angry%2C%20they%20think%20the%20teacher%20was%20getting%20a%20commission%20and%20scammed%20them.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20knew%20our%20parents%20would%20never%20let%20us%20go%20for%20a%20Rs.%207%2C000%20job%20outside%20of%20the%20village%20but%20he%20still%20gave%20us%20false%20promises%20and%20hopes%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20girls%20said.%20All%20four%20are%20back%20home%2C%20work%20in%20the%20household%20and%20are%20being%20pressured%20to%20be%20married.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Khadsaliya%20in%20Bhavnagar%20of%20Gujarat%20where%20gender%20biases%20restrict%20young%20women%20from%20several%20life%20opportunities%20including%20limited%20opportunities%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education%2C%20Malavi%20has%20managed%20to%20convince%20her%20parents.%20But%20without%20a%20job%2C%20she%20con%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etinues%20to%20polish%20diamonds%20at%20home%20%E2%80%93%20the%20cost%20for%20each%20diamond%20varies%20depending%20on%20its%20quality%20but%20can%20also%20be%20as%20less%20as%20Re%201%20per%20diamond.%20She%20makes%20Rs%20200%20a%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20village%20in%20Malkangiri%20in%20southern%20Odisha%20largely%20dependent%20on%20forest%20produce%20and%20rain%20fed%20agriculture%2C%20the%20community%20asks%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20we%20be%20sending%20our%20kids%20for%20education%3F%20There%20are%20no%20jobs!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarked%20by%20informalisation%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20jobs%2C%20lacunae%20in%20apprenticeship%20contracts%20and%20low%20regulation%20of%20industries%20themselves%20has%20left%20the%20students%20at%20the%20losing%20end%20scrounging%20for%20what%20was%20promised%20to%20them.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cskill-deficit%E2%80%9D%20narrative%20has%20invited%20an%20annual%20public%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores%20in%20running%203%2C500%20government%20ITIs%20along%20with%20the%20World%20Bank%20supported%20STRIVE%20scheme%20which%20pumps%20in%20an%20additional%20Rs%202%2C200%20crores.%20But%20still%2C%20unemployment%20persists.%20NITI%20Aayog%20reports%20that%20industries%20still%20complain%20of%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20technicians%20and%20the%20placement%20rate%20of%20ITIs%20remains%20low%20at%20less%20than%200.1%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20student%20in%20ITI%20Balasore%20captures%20the%20plight%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20we%20made%20to%20go%20from%20one%20degree%20to%20another%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20subjected%20to%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPriyanka%20Krishna%20is%20graduate%20of%20SOAS%2C%20University%20of%20London%20and%20works%20as%20a%20researcher%20in%20the%20field%20of%20education%20and%20development%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EBhawna%20Parmar%20is%20a%20graduate%20of%20Ambedkar%20University%2C%20Delhi%20and%20works%20as%20a%20researcher%20in%20the%20field%20of%20youth%20studies%20and%20education.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709728236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07083516%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fskill-india-unemployment-iti-apprenticeship-jobs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Across%20India%2C%20the%20Union%20government's%20stress%20on%20skilling%20and%20entrepreneurship%20makes%20mockery%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20young%20Indians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fskill-india-unemployment-iti-apprenticeship-jobs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nikki%20Haley%20to%20withdraw%20from%20Republican%20presidential%20race%20-%20without%20endorsing%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709723400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-nikki-haley-republican_6479550.jpg%3F20240305