d%20floral%20waste%2C%20she%20came%20across%20a%20small%20business%20near%20her%20house%20who%20used%20cow%20dung%20powder%20to%20make%20incense%20sticks.%20Could%20she%20do%C2%A0the%20same%20with%20flowers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20small%20space%20provided%20by%20her%20brother%2C%20Poonam%20set%20up%20her%20unit.%20From%20June%202019%2C%20she%20will%20get%20up%20at%205%20am%20and%20go%20to%20temples%20near%20her%20residence.%20There%2C%20she%20would%20request%20the%20staff%20to%20give%20her%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20obliged%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20mixed%20with%20other%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201242px)%20100vw%2C%201242px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poonam%20sells%20her%20products%20through%20exhibitions%20and%20her%20website%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913.jpeg%201242w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-300x199.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-500x331.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-768x509.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-150x99.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22823%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPoonam%20sells%20her%20products%20through%20exhibitions%20and%20her%20website.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%209%20am%2C%20she%20brought%20all%20the%20waste%20in%20her%20car%2C%20segregated%20it%20and%20dried%20it%20under%20the%20sun.%20In%20hopes%20of%20being%20able%20to%20experiment%20with%20these%20dried%20flowers%2C%20she%20faced%20her%20first%20hurdle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20drying%20the%20flowers%20for%20almost%20two%20months%2C%20I%20was%20going%20to%20powder%20them.%20I%20even%20bought%20a%20pulverizer%20machine%2C%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20factor%20in%20the%20weather%2C%20and%20the%20flowers%20got%20drenched%20in%20the%20rainfall.%20All%20my%20flowers%20were%20spoiled%20and%20I%20had%20to%20start%20all%20over%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20one%20to%20give%20up%2C%20she%20visited%20many%20temples%20again%2C%20and%20repeated%20the%20whole%20process.%20This%20time%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20successfully%20dry%20and%20powder%20the%20flowers.%20Using%20these%20powdered%20flowers%2C%20ghee%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98havan%E2%80%99%20products%2C%20and%20other%20ingredients%2C%20she%20tried%20her%20hand%20at%20making%20dhoop%20sticks.%20Through%20some%20permutations%20and%20combinations%2C%20and%20hours%20of%20working%2C%20she%20found%20the%20winning%20combination%20of%2016%20herbs%20sometime%20in%20September%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Janmashtami%202019.%20I%20took%20these%20dhoop%20sticks%20and%20gave%20them%20to%20the%20temple%20priest%20who%20supported%20me.%20He%20was%20so%20happy%20and%20promised%20to%20give%20me%20segregated%20floral%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20entrepreneur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20initially%20invested%20her%20savings%20into%20the%20business%2C%20Poonam%20also%20took%20a%20Mudra%20loan%20to%20support%20her%20venture.%C2%A0%