g%20to%20the%20test%20results%2C%20we%20guide%20them%20to%20pursue%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F120597%2Flearning-india-education-sattva%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20fields%20of%20interest.%20Although%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20vertical%2C%20we%20keep%20a%20very%20close%20watch%20on%20these%20students%20and%20extend%20our%20support%20whenever%20needed.%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20we%20have%20also%20helped%20our%20children%20get%20stable%20jobs%20with%20the%20help%20of%20our%20sponsors%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20builder%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Smita%20(name%20changed)%2C%20who%20was%20once%20rescued%20from%20child%20marriage%2C%20is%20now%20working%20in%20a%20non-banking%20financial%20company%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20nonprofit.%20She%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20this%20organisation%20since%20I%20was%205%20years%20old.%20Initially%2C%20they%20helped%20me%20enrol%20in%20a%20government%20school.%20After%20completing%20class%2010%2C%20when%20I%20went%20back%20to%20my%20hometown%2C%20I%20was%20informed%20that%20my%20marriage%20had%20been%20fixed%20with%20a%20man%20who%20was%2010%20years%20older%20than%20me.%20At%20my%20%3Cem%3Ehaldi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eceremony%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20team%20from%20the%20NGO%20came%20to%20my%20rescue%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20police%2C%20my%20marriage%20was%20stopped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20Pune%20and%20continued%20my%20higher%20studies%20till%20class%2012%20and%20secured%20a%20job%20in%20a%20bank.%20Whatever%20I%20am%20today%20is%20because%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20this%20NGO%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20long-term%20impact%20post-handholding%2C%20Manjusha%20says%2