ndia.com%2F315290%2Fbengal-modernist-jamini-roy-home-turned-into-private-single-artist-museum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowerful%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%E2%80%98inclusivity%E2%80%99.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20mural%20being%20crafted%20in%20the%20style%20of%20Rajasthani%20artisans%20allows%20the%20students%20to%20experience%20a%20sense%20of%20joy%20and%20belonging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20indoor%20art%20museum%20lets%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20marvellous%20artisanal%20works%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ekathputli%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20blue%20pottery%20and%20carpet%20making%20%E2%80%94%20have%20their%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20art%20workshop%20in%20close%20quarters%20features%20the%20artworks%20created%20by%20the%20students%20during%20the%20Sparsh%20initiative.%20This%20is%20accompanied%20by%20the%20braille%20text%20so%20that%20the%20kids%20can%20feel%20the%20visuals%20and%20simultaneously%20read%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForaying%20into%20this%20new%20territory%20of%20bringing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307819%2Fbengaluru-engineer-sohail-nargund-knits-to-bust-anxiety-breaks-stereotypes-on-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einclusivity%20into%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20easy.%20There%20were%20many%20new%20roads%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20because%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20spectrum%20of%20things%20which%20we%20perceive%20as%20normal%2C%20but%20are%20inaccessible%20to%20blind%20persons.%20But%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20textures%20played%20a%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Giulia%2C%20who%20shares%20what%20an%20%E2%80%9Ceducative%20experience%E2%80%9D%20it%20has%20been%20for%20all%20the%20individuals%20involved%20in%20the%20project.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20project%20required%20us%20to%20ask%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20and%20really%20break%20through%20what%20we%20knew%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3